**Highlights:** Gudzinevičiūtė won the inaugural women’s trap event in 2000 with a perfect finals score, shooting a Perazzi MX8:contentReference[oaicite:33]{index=33}. Her victory marked the expansion of Perazzi’s gold-medal legacy to women’s trap on its Olympic debut.
