The tester and fitter may need to discuss realistic POI ranges with the customer.', null, '4.1 Extreme POI Requests', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.K > 4. Edge Cases, Exceptions, and Caveats > 4.1 Extreme POI Requests', '["4-1-extreme-poi-requests","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-k-4-edge-cases-exceptions-and-caveats-4-1-extreme-poi-requests"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:57:15.866317+00', null), ('0482db78-c492-40f7-8e7a-defa5fc38d5f', 'e71c2213-11d3-4fbb-ad08-12dd9cb1fbe1', '15', '49', '- Maintaining **safe gun handling** and range discipline while:

- Test-firing many guns per day.  
  - Switching loads and guns frequently.

- Using ear and eye protection consistently.', null, '3.3.5 Safety & Range Procedure', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.K > 3. Main Content > 3.3 Core Knowledge & Skills > 3.3.5 Safety & Range Procedure', '["3-3-5-safety-range-procedure","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-k-3-main-content-3-3-core-knowledge-skills-3-3-5-safety-range-procedure"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:57:15.866317+00', null), ('0501f0c2-8511-456f-9b81-821dec130e4f', '8078a4a0-2d04-41fd-bd01-ecfc4c710fbb', '0', '50', '### Ennio Mattarelli
**Country:** Italy
**Event:** Men’s Trap (Olympic Trap)
**Medal:** Gold
**Olympics:** 1964 Tokyo
**Perazzi platform:** Custom Perazzi Sidelock ("Model SHO")
