- Depth is chosen so initial feel is grippy but not painful.', null, '3.4.4 Point vs Slightly Flat-Topped Diamonds', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.G > 3. Main Content > 3.4 Decisions & Trade-Offs > 3.4.4 Point vs Slightly Flat-Topped Diamonds', '["3-4-4-point-vs-slightly-flat-topped-diamonds","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-g-3-main-content-3-4-decisions-trade-offs-3-4-4-point-vs-slightly-flat-topped-diamonds"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:55:44.833658+00', null), ('0d3ff27a-94c8-4da4-b0be-bc231094a562', '5eba6cac-e507-407b-80c3-b76bdb3f3e89', '10', '32', '- **Purpose:** Tell the story of Perazzi—factory, founders, champions, and the long arc of success.
