  Distance from the trigger to the center of the butt pad/plate.

- **Drop**  
  Vertical distance between the line of sight and the comb/heel of the stock, determining how high or low the eye sits in relation to the rib.

- **Cast**  
  Lateral bend of the stock (e.g., cast-off for right-handed shooters), affecting how the eye aligns over the rib.

- **Point of Impact (POI)**  
  Where the shot pattern centers relative to the aiming point (e.g., 50/50, 60/40, 70/30 high pattern).

- **Balance Point**  
  The location along the gun’s length where it balances when supported. Often near the hinge pin or slightly forward on Perazzi O/Us.

- **Handling**  
  The subjective feel of how the gun mounts, swings, and recovers, influenced by weight distribution, geometry, and recoil behavior.', null, '2.2 Fit, Balance & Handling', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part III: Cross-Cutting Systems > 2. Key Concepts & Glossary > 2.2 Fit, Balance & Handling', '["2-2-fit-balance-handling","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-iii-cross-cutting-systems-2-key-concepts-glossary-2-2-fit-balance-handling"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:58:22.014078+00', null), ('0f738ea2-bdeb-484c-a5ff-71d23022553c', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '150', '238', 'Model name: MX12 SCO Gold Sideplates | Base model: mx12 | Platform: MX | Category: competition | Disciplines: Skeet, Sporting | Engraving Grade: SCO Gold Sideplates | Combo configuration: yes | Gauges: 12ga | Barrel configuration style: over-under | Trigger: fixed | Trigger springs: coil | Rib: fixed | Rib style: flat, step, ramp', null, '### MX12 SCO Gold Sideplates', 'Models > MX12 SCO Gold Sideplates', '["model-details","mx12-sco-gold-sideplates","platform:mx"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('0f73c830-c757-4d54-96df-c564f7336b5d', '8078a4a0-2d04-41fd-bd01-ecfc4c710fbb', '12', '50', '### Giovanni Pellielo
