For questions like "Where do I send my gun?" or "How do I get service?", this is the anchor.', null, '2.3.6 Service & Support', 'PerazziGPT v2 – Source Corpus Manifest (User-Facing Site Overview) > 2. Site Structure & Area Concepts > 2.3 Site Area Concepts > 2.3.6 Service & Support', '["2-3-6-service-support","perazzigpt-v2-source-corpus-manifest-user-facing-site-overview-2-site-structure-area-concepts-2-3-site-area-concepts-2-3-6-service-support"]', '["Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:59:09.736657+00', null), ('13c37d5c-9e74-476a-8854-cd48acb81bfd', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '11', '238', 'Model name: High Tech | Base model: high-tech | Platform: HT | Category: competition | Disciplines: Trap | Engraving Grade: Standard | Combo configuration: no | Gauges: 12ga | Barrel configuration style: top-single | Trigger: removable | Trigger springs: flat, coil | Rib: fixed | Rib style: flat, step, ramp', null, '### High Tech', 'Models > High Tech', '["model-details","high-tech","platform:ht"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('13f0e31f-ee05-4024-a65f-40a6f7ad9df3', '4ae532ea-bef9-47fe-9bd9-051858902e2f', '14', '23', '- Mentally picture a Perazzi O/U broken down into major assemblies:
  - **Receiver / Action** – removable trigger group, safety, top lever, locking bolt, hinge pins/trunnions.  
  - **Barrels** – monobloc, tubes, ribs, ejectors, chokes.  
