- When discussing any part (e.g., locking bolt engaging the monobloc), **place it on this mental diagram**.
- Treat Part II as a guided tour through this exploded view: each station is responsible for one or more pieces.', null, '3.3.1 Shotgun Anatomy Diagram', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part V: Learning Map for the Reader > 3. Main Content > 3.3 Mental Models & Diagrams > 3.3.1 Shotgun Anatomy Diagram', '["3-3-1-shotgun-anatomy-diagram","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-v-learning-map-for-the-reader-3-main-content-3-3-mental-models-diagrams-3-3-1-shotgun-anatomy-diagram"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:58:59.884559+00', null), ('13f46abf-6fd8-4db3-9730-1fea256c0370', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '202', '238', 'Model name: MX410 SC3 Sideplates | Base model: mx410 | Platform: MX | Category: game | Disciplines: Game | Engraving Grade: SC3 Sideplates | Combo configuration: no | Gauges: 410ga | Barrel configuration style: over-under | Trigger: fixed | Trigger springs: coil | Rib: fixed', null, '### MX410 SC3 Sideplates', 'Models > MX410 SC3 Sideplates', '["model-details","mx410-sc3-sideplates","platform:mx"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('141c72a2-b28d-4043-b137-b0deb4ab4633', '40639b0a-dab7-48fe-8f4f-a017a331ec3e', '39', '45', '- Some steel batches may respond differently to standard bluing formulas (e.g., color shifts, slower rusting).  
- Finisher may adjust solution strength, number of cycles, or process parameters.', null, '4.1 Unusual Alloys or Batches', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.H > 4. Edge Cases, Exceptions, and Caveats > 4.1 Unusual Alloys or Batches', '["4-1-unusual-alloys-or-batches","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-h-4-edge-cases-exceptions-and-caveats-4-1-unusual-alloys-or-batches"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:56:02.508279+00', null), ('1457b640-56a3-4dd2-9ee9-dad100fcfccb', '30dc5da6-b9ed-450e-8736-4a6dfce0983a', '34', '40', '- Some clients request adjustable comb systems, either initially or after trying the gun.  
- Installing these requires cutting the comb and adding posts in a way that maintains strength and aesthetics.

**Caveat:**  
- On brand-new, bespoke guns, fixed stocks are often preferred; adjustable combs are reserved for specific use cases or later modifications.', null, '4.1 Adjustable Combs & Retrofits', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.F > 4. Edge Cases, Exceptions, and Caveats > 4.1 Adjustable Combs & Retrofits', '["4-1-adjustable-combs-retrofits","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-f-4-edge-cases-exceptions-and-caveats-4-1-adjustable-combs-retrofits"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:55:32.068221+00', null), ('14612042-21f5-4c62-b475-e7c8e2fbb543', '1e2052a5-ee5e-4421-83c1-cf4e7172cbf2', '10', '45', '- **Finished Stock & Fore-end**  
  - Fully sealed, colored (if desired), and rubbed to final sheen.  
  - Pores filled or left with a controlled open texture according to specification.  
  - Checkering sealed lightly but **not clogged**, with sharp diamonds intact.

- **Matched Wood Set**  
  - Stock and fore-end matched in tone and sheen; visual continuity across all wood parts.

- **Prepared Functional Surfaces**  
  - Comb and cheek area finished to comfortable, low-glare feel.  
  - Grip and fore-end surfaces finished in coordination with checkering for secure grasp.  
  - Butt area fully finished and integrated with recoil pad or buttplate.

- **Stable, Cured Finish**  
  - Finish cured sufficiently that it will not imprint easily or peel under normal handling.  
  - If oil-based, may continue to harden over time but is ready for assembly and use.

---', null, '3.2.2 Outputs', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.I > 3. Main Content > 3.2 Inputs & Outputs > 3.2.2 Outputs', '["3-2-2-outputs","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-i-3-main-content-3-2-inputs-outputs-3-2-2-outputs"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:56:22.593132+00', null), ('14632f63-d7ed-44fa-a61a-6b6acfed333e', '0894113c-c061-44ea-aa24-5dbe961f9a09', '32', '51', '- **Description:** Some areas cut deeper than others; diamonds show inconsistent point sharpness, or flat tops where insufficiently cut.  
- **Diagnosis:**  
  - Visual: some diamonds reflect light differently (flat vs sharp).  
  - Tactile: grip feels patchy, with smoother or rougher areas.  
- **Mitigation & Repair:**  
  - Additional passes in shallower areas to equalize depth.  
  - Avoid over-deepening local spots that would weaken diamonds; if unavoidable, blend surrounding area to similar depth.', null, '3.6.3 Uneven Depth & Flat Diamonds', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.G > 3. Main Content > 3.6 Failure Modes & Diagnosis > 3.6.3 Uneven Depth & Flat Diamonds', '["3-6-3-uneven-depth-flat-diamonds","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-g-3-main-content-3-6-failure-modes-diagnosis-3-6-3-uneven-depth-flat-diamonds"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:55:44.833658+00', null), ('1466597b-5dd1-4592-baf6-fe31e56b6950', '0894113c-c061-44ea-aa24-5dbe961f9a09', '38', '51', 'Mastery in checkering is **quiet and disciplined**; it reveals itself in the ease and consistency of the finished panels.', null, '3.7 What Mastery Looks Like', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.G > 3. Main Content > 3.7 What Mastery Looks Like', '["3-7-what-mastery-looks-like","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-g-3-main-content-3-7-what-mastery-looks-like"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:55:44.833658+00', null), ('14ae8232-5ec2-4e42-acc0-c8b28caa08b5', '6a033257-810e-408f-bcd1-5e0ba6cb7594', '0', '32', '- Source: Internal Perazzi USA Document - The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun
