**Highlights:** Rodríguez won Cuba’s first-ever Olympic shooting medal (skeet bronze in 2004) using a Perazzi MX8:contentReference[oaicite:94]{index=94}. His dramatic shoot-off victory for bronze was aided by the MX8’s quick swing and reliability. This achievement put Cuba on the Olympic shotgun medal map and did so with a Perazzi in hand.
