It focuses on:

- What makes Perazzi competition shotguns distinct in heritage, philosophy, and construction.
- The **architectural hallmarks** of Perazzi O/U designs (action, trigger group, barrel system).
- How Perazzi compares to mass-market manufacturers and traditional “best gun” makers.
- A high-level **end-to-end production process map** from customer specification to final inspection.

This is **Part I** of a multi-part handbook. Later parts will “zoom in” on each production stage and the craftspeople who execute it.

---', null, '1. High-Level Overview', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part I: Product & System Overview > 1. High-Level Overview', '["1-high-level-overview","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-i-product-system-overview-1-high-level-overview"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:54:11.853745+00', null), ('2658d12e-77b0-4d82-8556-2d2d1834e903', '30dc5da6-b9ed-450e-8736-4a6dfce0983a', '35', '40', '- After live test-firing, shooter may request:  
  - Significant change in comb height.  
  - Noticeable shift in cast or toe.

**Caveat:**  
- Small adjustments can be made by reshaping or mild bending, but large changes may be constrained by remaining wood thickness and structural limits.  
- At times, starting a new stock is more appropriate than pushing one beyond safe adjustment margins.', null, '4.2 Extreme Fit Adjustments Post-Test', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.F > 4. Edge Cases, Exceptions, and Caveats > 4.2 Extreme Fit Adjustments Post-Test', '["4-2-extreme-fit-adjustments-post-test","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-f-4-edge-cases-exceptions-and-caveats-4-2-extreme-fit-adjustments-post-test"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:55:32.068221+00', null), ('26ae669c-b5da-4e49-b4a8-70f5d76d5fe7', '8078a4a0-2d04-41fd-bd01-ecfc4c710fbb', '41', '50', '### Steven Scott
