- Perazzi UK – High Tech introduction (mentions Olympic podium use):contentReference[oaicite:147]{index=147}', null, '### Steven Scott', 'Olympic Medals > Steven Scott', '["olympic-medals","steven-scott"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Loyalist","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:20.792823+00', null), ('26eb7202-7768-483a-9579-35407b0027f2', 'dadad96d-904b-4c92-af84-aba4f15f7e85', '4', '48', '- **Length of Pull (LOP)**  
  - Distance from trigger face to center of butt (heel or pad midpoint); primary length dimension of stock.

- **Drop at Comb / Drop at Heel**  
  - Vertical distance from the sighting plane (rib axis) to the comb and heel, respectively.  
  - Determines how high the shooter’s eye sits relative to rib.

- **Cast-Off / Cast-On**  
  - Lateral offset of the stock from the barrel/action centerline.  
  - Cast-off: butt moved to the right for right-handed shooters.  
  - Cast-on: butt moved to the left for left-handed shooters.

- **Pitch**  
  - Angle of the butt plate relative to the bore line; influences how the stock sits in the shoulder and how recoil is distributed.

- **Heel and Toe**  
  - Upper and lower corners of the butt end of the stock.

- **Grip / Wrist Shape**  
  - Geometry of the area where the shooting hand holds the stock; may include palm swell.

- **Monte Carlo Comb**  
  - Raised comb structure often used on trap stocks to maintain higher eye position.', null, '2.3 Fit & Geometry Terms', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.E > 2. Key Concepts & Glossary > 2.3 Fit & Geometry Terms', '["2-3-fit-geometry-terms","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-e-2-key-concepts-glossary-2-3-fit-geometry-terms"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:55:17.919795+00', null), ('2760a8e0-63cc-4d4c-b697-4118ea764871', '0894113c-c061-44ea-aa24-5dbe961f9a09', '10', '51', 'The checkerer’s work requires **precision, rhythm, and visual sensitivity**.', null, '3.3 Core Knowledge & Skills', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.G > 3. Main Content > 3.3 Core Knowledge & Skills', '["3-3-core-knowledge-skills","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-g-3-main-content-3-3-core-knowledge-skills"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:55:44.833658+00', null), ('2761e8fd-5ea3-4d5f-a828-4b0c554dd399', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '222', '238', 'Model name: MX8 SCO Gold | Base model: mx8 | Platform: MX | Category: competition | Disciplines: Skeet, Sporting | Engraving Grade: SCO Gold | Combo configuration: yes | Gauges: 12ga | Barrel configuration style: over-under | Trigger: removable | Trigger springs: flat, coil | Rib: fixed | Rib style: flat, step, ramp', null, '### MX8 SCO Gold', 'Models > MX8 SCO Gold', '["model-details","mx8-sco-gold","platform:mx"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('2791481c-5600-4358-a648-a95527d0f86d', 'c5b4fa4d-9f28-4908-a706-fbdc7cefdf94', '40', '53', '- Resist the temptation to chase textbook numbers when the shooter is already performing well.  
- Recognize when additional changes would mainly add complexity rather than benefit.  
- Prefer stable, repeatable configurations that shooters can internalize over time.', null, '3.7.2 Knowing When Good is Good Enough', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.L > 3. Main Content > 3.7 What Mastery Looks Like > 3.7.2 Knowing When Good is Good Enough', '["3-7-2-knowing-when-good-is-good-enough","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-l-3-main-content-3-7-what-mastery-looks-like-3-7-2-knowing-when-good-is-good-enough"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:57:33.590816+00', null), ('27b5ecd0-4d66-42b6-8c86-29bf9bc33934', '1ae4b60f-6ad5-4475-9eb9-cabf6b0e829c', '48', '56', '> After assembling a custom Perazzi, Luigi, a senior assembler, begins his well-practiced twelve-point check.  
> He closes the gun and watches the top lever settle just right of center. He opens it, feeling the hammers cock with a smooth, even resistance. With snap caps in place, he pulls the trigger—one sharp click. He opens the gun and hears both ejectors ping in perfect unison as the snap caps leap clear.  
>  
> He repeats the test with the barrel selector reversed: same crisp break, same clean ejection. Next, he simulates recoil with a firm tap on the butt, testing the inertia system. Satisfied, he measures trigger weights, checks headspace with gauges, and inspects every screw slot under bright light.  
> Only when every item on his list is met—and the gun feels, in his hands, like a true Perazzi—does he sign off and send it on to pattern testing.', null, '3.7.6 Example Vignette: Luigi’s Twelve-Point Check (Composite, Illustrative)', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.J > 3. Main Content > 3.7 What Mastery Looks Like > 3.7.6 Example Vignette: Luigi’s Twelve-Point Check (Composite, Illustrative)', '["3-7-6-example-vignette-luigi-s-twelve-point-check-composite-illustrative","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-j-3-main-content-3-7-what-mastery-looks-like-3-7-6-example-vignette-luigi-s-twelve-point-check-composite-illustrative"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:56:46.826724+00', null), ('27d232ac-ad86-46e0-9326-a2d33ddf50a7', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '208', '238', 'Model name: MX8 | Base model: mx8 | Platform: MX | Category: competition | Disciplines: Trap | Engraving Grade: Standard | Combo configuration: yes | Gauges: 12ga | Barrel configuration style: top-single | Trigger: removable | Trigger springs: flat, coil | Rib: fixed | Rib style: flat, step, ramp', null, '### MX8', 'Models > MX8', '["model-details","mx8","platform:mx"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('28282e5b-45c4-4a46-b206-4d56f8e8a444', '38271655-0cf1-46de-9724-9413638fc3cc', '0', '1', '- **McKnight Gunsmithing**  
