Key early-career milestones:

- Started shooting competitively at age 8.  
- Won his first major title at 16, becoming the youngest ever to take an HOA at a major championship[25].  
- By 14, he had already captained Team USA, setting an age record that set the tone for his career[26].

The source states that David is a 14-time world champion across various disciplines and age categories[27][28]. His accolades include:

- World FITASC Champion.  
- Three-time U.S. Open Sporting Clays Champion.  
- Four Professional Clay Shooting Association (PCSA) tour titles[27].  
- Representation of the United States on 15 international teams, ranging from junior world championships to senior world titles[29][30].

David is described as a “thinking man’s shooter,” holding a degree in marketing and psychology and viewing clay shooting as both art and science[31][32]. His psychological and philosophical approach to shooting is mentioned in connection with his coaching and a popular podcast[33].

Additional achievements and notes:

- Youngest Master class shooter at 12.  
- First to shoot 100/100 at 14[34].  
- Multiple world titles as both junior and adult[29].  
- Recognized for sportsmanship and innovative vision for the sport.

He is also described as founder of The Champions Network, an initiative aimed at growing shooting sports through media[35][36]. Through roles as competitor, coach, and entrepreneur, the source emphasizes that David remains “at heart, the wide-eyed kid who fell in love with a shotgun,” channeling that passion into everything he does.', null, '3.1.4.1 Biography & Background', 'Perazzi USA Team & Supported Shooters (AI-Optimized Reference) > 3. Main Content > 3.1 Sponsored Shooters (Perazzi USA Team) > 3.1.4 David Radulovich – Sporting Clays (Sponsored Shooter) > 3.1.4.1 Biography & Background', '["3-1-4-1-biography-background","perazzi-usa-team-supported-shooters-ai-optimized-reference-3-main-content-3-1-sponsored-shooters-perazzi-usa-team-3-1-4-david-radulovich-sporting-clays-sponsored-shooter-3-1-4-1-biography-background"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:51:56.586148+00', null), ('2a0dcc1f-f7dc-4ff0-b41e-fc2075b3fd40', '00ee41e2-2a64-4498-9321-fde7e5df53f0', '25', '51', '- **Bright Lighting & Magnification**  
