t","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('2de88ce7-f34c-41ab-aa88-5a216b2bcaac', '67ca387d-48bc-4047-9404-209a02645c52', '31', '39', '- Many critical skills are **tacit, not fully codified**:
