l, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('30afa6b0-1d60-4df7-aaf6-bc174e7b32b4', '40639b0a-dab7-48fe-8f4f-a017a331ec3e', '16', '45', '- Ensuring pre-finish polishing **supports engraving** rather than erasing it:  
  - Major polishing done before engraving where possible.  
  - After engraving, final polish is extremely controlled to avoid rounding scrolls or lettering.

- For coin-finish receivers:  
  - Maintaining contrast between engraved backgrounds and raised scroll by controlled polishing or slight burnishing.', null, '3.3.5 Protection of Engraving', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.H > 3. Main Content > 3.3 Core Knowledge & Skills > 3.3.5 Protection of Engraving', '["3-3-5-protection-of-engraving","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-h-3-main-content-3-3-core-knowledge-skills-3-3-5-protection-of-engraving"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:56:02.508279+00', null), ('30fa0c55-bfba-40da-bd20-e524adee99e9', '0894113c-c061-44ea-aa24-5dbe961f9a09', '44', '51', '> **Example vignette (composite, illustrative):**  
> A VIP customer requests a slightly different grip pattern on a new Perazzi—a double-line border instead of the usual single line. One of the senior checkering technicians accepts the stock without fanfare. After the standard pattern is cut, she freehands the second border line, following the curve of the grip by eye. There are no templates for this variation; she trusts her sense of spacing and flow. When she finishes, the double border looks perfectly parallel and evenly spaced, as though it had always been part of the design. To an observer, it seems routine; to another checkerer, it’s a subtle demonstration of mastery.

---', null, '3.7.6 Example Vignette: The Double Border', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.G > 3. Main Content > 3.7 What Mastery Looks Like > 3.7.6 Example Vignette: The Double Border', '["3-7-6-example-vignette-the-double-border","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-g-3-main-content-3-7-what-mastery-looks-like-3-7-6-example-vignette-the-double-border"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:55:44.833658+00', null), ('314e4dcd-b5a6-4d37-8735-454b082b31ca', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '93', '238', 'Model name: High Tech S 5 SC3 Gold | Base model: high-tech-s-5 | Platform: HT | Category: competition | Disciplines: All Disciplines | Engraving Grade: SC3 Gold | Combo configuration: no | Gauges: 12ga, 20ga | Barrel configuration style: over-under | Trigger: fixed | Trigger springs: coil | Rib: adjustable | Rib notches: 5-notch adjustable | Rib height: 24.0 mm | Rib style: notch', null, '### High Tech S 5 SC3 Gold', 'Models > High Tech S 5 SC3 Gold', '["model-details","high-tech-s-5-sc3-gold","platform:ht"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('315434d4-ee5a-4a40-b52b-128249d9e83c', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '170', '238', 'Model name: MX20 SC3 Sideplates | Base model: mx20 | Platform: MX | Category: mixed | Disciplines: Sporting, Game | Engraving Grade: SC3 Sideplates | Combo configuration: no | Gauges: 20ga | Barrel configuration style: over-under | Trigger: fixed | Trigger springs: coil | Rib: fixed', null, '### MX20 SC3 Sideplates', 'Models > MX20 SC3 Sideplates', '["model-details","mx20-sc3-sideplates","platform:mx"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('321f1f24-a39c-47ba-adc5-581c2b0462f8', '00ee41e2-2a64-4498-9321-fde7e5df53f0', '5', '51', '- **Safety Check**  
  - Verification that with safety **on**, the gun does not fire; with safety **off**, the triggers function correctly.

- **Trigger & Ejector Sanity Check**  
  - Final dry‑fire and snap‑cap test confirming triggers reset and ejectors function as in earlier mechanical QC.

- **Accessory Completeness**  
  - Confirmation that all items promised with gun are present (e.g., spare firing pins and springs, choke tubes and wrench, stock wrench, manual, warranty card, oil bottle, etc.).', null, '2.4 Functional Concepts', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.M > 2. Key Concepts & Glossary > 2.4 Functional Concepts', '["2-4-functional-concepts","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-m-2-key-concepts-glossary-2-4-functional-concepts"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:57:55.761534+00', null), ('3358b32f-b4e7-4a39-a5ee-d3ef27af8b01', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '135', '238', 'Model name: MX10 | Base model: mx10 | Platform: MX | Category: competition | Disciplines: Trap | Engraving Grade: Standard | Combo configuration: yes | Gauges: 12ga | Barrel configuration style: top-single | Trigger: removable | Trigger springs: flat, coil | Rib: adjustable | Rib notches: 4-notch adjustable | Rib height: 17.0 mm | Rib style: notch', null, '### MX10', 'Models > MX10', '["model-details","mx10","platform:mx"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('33c5aa1c-ab36-49f3-85bb-8811b56b8090', '82a899f9-2019-4029-b599-221316624acd', '37', '38', '- **1. High-Level Overview** – Purpose of the document and organizational structure.  
- **2. Key Concepts & Glossary** – Canonical definitions for athlete categories, disciplines (as named), abbreviations, and name canonicalization.  
- **3.1 Sponsored Shooters (Perazzi USA Team)**  
