---', null, '3.4.6 Fore-end Style & Customization', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.E > 3. Main Content > 3.4 Decisions & Trade-Offs > 3.4.6 Fore-end Style & Customization', '["3-4-6-fore-end-style-customization","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-e-3-main-content-3-4-decisions-trade-offs-3-4-6-fore-end-style-customization"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:55:17.919795+00', null), ('44137754-c461-4c8d-a54d-784d1e2198e9', '00ee41e2-2a64-4498-9321-fde7e5df53f0', '18', '51', '- Use **judgment** to decide:  
