- Uses spacers to adjust LOP and pitch without cutting wood when possible.  
- Fits spacers and pads cleanly so they follow the butt outline and remain flush.  
- Performs quick pad modifications (e.g., rounding pad toe or heel) to prevent pad catching on mount.', null, '3.3.4 Recoil Pad Fitting & Pad Adjustments', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.L > 3. Main Content > 3.3 Core Knowledge & Skills > 3.3.4 Recoil Pad Fitting & Pad Adjustments', '["3-3-4-recoil-pad-fitting-pad-adjustments","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-l-3-main-content-3-3-core-knowledge-skills-3-3-4-recoil-pad-fitting-pad-adjustments"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:57:33.590816+00', null), ('48293078-f245-48e9-887e-5caf3a1cd12a', 'fae85afb-4054-48f2-a2a6-8d756c851b62', '5', '32', '- **Founded**: 1957 by **Daniele Perazzi**, in Italy.  
- **Mission**: Blend **best-of-British craft principles** (fine gunmaking, aesthetic sensibility) with **modern manufacturing** methods (precision machining, metallurgy) to produce shotguns of exceptional performance and durability.  
- **Disciplines**: Primarily clay target sports – **Olympic trap**, **skeet**, and **sporting clays**.

Perazzi’s shotguns are designed from the outset as **competition machines**, not decor pieces:

- Built for **very high round counts** (hundreds of thousands of shells over a lifetime).[1]
- Emphasis on **reliability, pattern consistency, and recoil mitigation**.
- Capable of being **rebuilt** via replacement of wear parts (springs, locking lugs, hinge pins) over time.', null, '3.1.1 Origins and Mission', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part I: Product & System Overview > 3. Main Content > 3.1 Perazzi’s Competition Shotguns and Their Heritage > 3.1.1 Origins and Mission', '["3-1-1-origins-and-mission","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-i-product-system-overview-3-main-content-3-1-perazzi-s-competition-shotguns-and-their-heritage-3-1-1-origins-and-mission"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:54:11.853745+00', null), ('48483d21-ddc6-4cc6-9252-2f2fd72426c1', 'c5b4fa4d-9f28-4908-a706-fbdc7cefdf94', '38', '53', '- **Symptoms:** Final stock dimensions or adjustments not captured accurately in records.  
