  - **Stock Blank Selection & Rough Shaping Station (Part II.E)** – supplies rough stock and fore-end with geometry and oversize allowances.  
  - **Trigger Group & Lockwork Assembly Station (Part II.D)** – influences trigger reach, guard inletting, and clearance for internal mechanisms.

