---', null, '0. Metadata', 'Perazzi Brand Ethos & Personality – AI Reference > 0. Metadata', '["0-metadata","perazzi-brand-ethos-personality-ai-reference-0-metadata"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:51:25.853025+00', null), ('4997ae4c-e71c-498a-b5bd-b5205dd0ff0c', '6a033257-810e-408f-bcd1-5e0ba6cb7594', '31', '32', '- **1. High-Level Overview** – Scope and purpose of the Design & Specification station.  
- **2. Key Concepts & Glossary** – Definitions of roles, fit dimensions, barrel concepts, actions, triggers, and quality terms.  
  - 2.1 Roles and Stages.  
