- **3. Main Content** – Detailed description of how the station operates.  
  - 3.1 Station Purpose & Success Criteria.  
  - 3.2 Inputs & Outputs.  
  - 3.3 Core Knowledge & Skills.  
  - 3.4 Typical Decisions & Trade-Offs.  
    - 3.4.1 Barrel Length vs Handling.  
