- **Other options**:[132][133]  
  - Multi-choke systems, special ribs, glove grips, adjustable buttplates, and barrel porting may add additional cost.', null, '3.8.3 Upgrades and Cost Drivers', 'Perazzi Brand Bible – AI Reference > 3. Main Content > 3.8 Pricing Structure and Value > 3.8.3 Upgrades and Cost Drivers', '["3-8-3-upgrades-and-cost-drivers","perazzi-brand-bible-ai-reference-3-main-content-3-8-pricing-structure-and-value-3-8-3-upgrades-and-cost-drivers"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:51:07.263026+00', null), ('4cfb5a93-40d9-49a4-a4ce-ea9a907062a0', '30dc5da6-b9ed-450e-8736-4a6dfce0983a', '15', '40', '- Maintains **razor-sharp tools** to avoid crushed fibers and tear-out.  
- Uses specialized scrapers and rifflers to refine difficult internal curves and external transitions.  
- Understands **pre-finish techniques**:  
  - Raising grain with light wetting and re-sanding to reduce grain-raising during finishing.  
  - Avoiding contamination of wood with oils, glue, or dirt that can hinder stain and finish absorption.  
- Controls edge sharpness:  
