- Wants a gun that feels like a **legitimate partner in improvement**.', null, '3.4.1 Core Motivation', 'V2_Audience-Psychology-and-Archetypes.md > 3. Archetypes – Detailed Descriptions > 3.4 Achiever > 3.4.1 Core Motivation', '["3-4-1-core-motivation","v2-audience-psychology-and-archetypes-md-3-archetypes-detailed-descriptions-3-4-achiever-3-4-1-core-motivation"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:51:40.516062+00', null), ('5042bc5d-5a10-4825-9d4e-98acc93710e5', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '114', '238', 'Model name: High Tech SC3 | Base model: high-tech | Platform: HT | Category: competition | Disciplines: Skeet, Sporting | Engraving Grade: SC3 | Combo configuration: yes | Gauges: 12ga | Barrel configuration style: over-under | Trigger: removable | Trigger springs: flat, coil | Rib: fixed | Rib style: flat, step, ramp', null, '### High Tech SC3', 'Models > High Tech SC3', '["model-details","high-tech-sc3","platform:ht"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('50844bc0-eaaa-4a64-a4d7-d15f470175e6', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '224', '238', 'Model name: MX8 SCO Gold Sideplates | Base model: mx8 | Platform: MX | Category: competition | Disciplines: Trap | Engraving Grade: SCO Gold Sideplates | Combo configuration: yes | Gauges: 12ga | Barrel configuration style: top-single | Trigger: removable | Trigger springs: flat, coil | Rib: fixed | Rib style: flat, step, ramp', null, '### MX8 SCO Gold Sideplates', 'Models > MX8 SCO Gold Sideplates', '["model-details","mx8-sco-gold-sideplates","platform:mx"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('510115be-2207-4f2f-922e-123addfa5d40', '536080f1-89e0-4124-9514-2ba022ce8a4b', '32', '36', 'The original text does not explicitly list edge cases, but it implies important constraints on how the brand should **not** be represented. For AI usage, treat the following as guardrails derived from the ethos:

- **No Price-Based Positioning**  
  Do not frame Perazzi as a discount, entry-level, or price-driven brand. Its ethos is anchored in **exclusivity, craftsmanship, and legacy**, not affordability or deals.

- **Lead Times and Availability as Intentional**  
  Do not present lead times or limited availability as defects or apologize for them. When relevant, acknowledge them honestly and gently frame them as a natural result of focused, artisanal production and the brand’s commitment to depth over volume.

- **Avoid Loud or Flashy Tone**  
  Do not use aggressive, shouty, or hype-driven language. The correct tone is **quiet, confident, and reverent**.

- **Do Not Flatten the Narrative into Pure Specs**  
  While technical excellence is assumed, the brand story should not read like a bare spec sheet. It should preserve the **emotional and philosophical framing**.

- **Do Not Treat Sponsorship as Commodity**  
  Perazzi’s approach to events is based on **experiences and belonging**, not logo placement volume. Avoid describing brand activity as generic sponsorship without the experiential and transformative dimension.

- **Maintain Emotional Depth Across Audiences**  
  Even when speaking to prestige buyers or achievers, the language should retain **depth and sincerity**, not drift into hollow luxury clichés.

---', null, '4. Edge Cases, Exceptions, and Caveats', 'Perazzi Brand Ethos & Personality – AI Reference > 4. Edge Cases, Exceptions, and Caveats', '["4-edge-cases-exceptions-and-caveats","perazzi-brand-ethos-personality-ai-reference-4-edge-cases-exceptions-and-caveats"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:51:25.853025+00', null), ('51066de9-ce19-41aa-ab5d-4a2f2217a246', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '132', '238', 'Model name: High Tech X RS | Base model: high-tech-rs | Platform: HT | Category: competition | Disciplines: Trap | Engraving Grade: X | Combo configuration: yes | Gauges: 12ga | Barrel configuration style: unsingle | Trigger: removable | Trigger springs: flat, coil | Rib: adjustable | Rib notches: 4-notch adjustable | Rib height: 10.0 mm | Rib style: notch', null, '### High Tech X RS', 'Models > High Tech X RS', '["model-details","high-tech-x-rs","platform:ht"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('510875cc-1d4a-4cc2-8c25-39d7cba85cc1', '0894113c-c061-44ea-aa24-5dbe961f9a09', '33', '51', '- **Description:** Patterns on left and right sides of grip/fore-end differ in line count, coverage, or border placement.  
- **Diagnosis:** Visual comparison and counting lines/pattern rows.  
- **Mitigation & Repair:**  
  - Use careful pre-layout and counting to prevent.  
  - If discovered early, adjust border placement or final edge lines subtly to restore apparent symmetry.', null, '3.6.4 Side-to-Side Pattern Mismatch', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.G > 3. Main Content > 3.6 Failure Modes & Diagnosis > 3.6.4 Side-to-Side Pattern Mismatch', '["3-6-4-side-to-side-pattern-mismatch","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-g-3-main-content-3-6-failure-modes-diagnosis-3-6-4-side-to-side-pattern-mismatch"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:55:44.833658+00', null), ('515cfa06-e9c2-43aa-90eb-77f0a237c53d', '30dc5da6-b9ed-450e-8736-4a6dfce0983a', '7', '40', 'The **Stock Inletting & Final Shaping station**:

- Transforms rough-cut stock and fore-end into **precisely fitted, fully shaped furniture**.
- Marries wood to the exact **action, tangs, trigger guard, and fore-end iron** for a given serial number.
- Finalizes the external form so that the shooter’s **fit measurements** become a tangible, ergonomic reality.
- Prepares surfaces and edges to a standard suitable for checkering and finishing.', null, '3.1.1 Purpose', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.F > 3. Main Content > 3.1 Station Purpose & Success Criteria > 3.1.1 Purpose', '["3-1-1-purpose","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-f-3-main-content-3-1-station-purpose-success-criteria-3-1-1-purpose"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:55:32.068221+00', null), ('51caaa80-2c28-49a5-a720-1af082a50dfa', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '234', '238', 'Model name: High Tech CO | Base model: high-tech-co | Platform: HT | Category: competition | Disciplines: Trap | Engraving Grade: Standard | Combo configuration: no | Gauges: 12ga | Barrel configuration style: top-single | Trigger: removable | Trigger springs: flat, coil | Rib: fixed | Rib height: 2.0 mm | Rib style: ramp', null, '### High Tech CO', 'Models > High Tech CO', '["model-details","high-tech-co","platform:ht"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('522ff8e1-452b-4e17-9bf8-ce9973a0d600', '0894113c-c061-44ea-aa24-5dbe961f9a09', '42', '51', '- Masters calmly handle unusual requests (e.g., a double border not standard for that model) and integrate them seamlessly.  
- They can adjust layouts mid-stream to preserve visual balance without drawing attention to the adjustment.', null, '3.7.4 Adaptability & On-the-Fly Corrections', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.G > 3. Main Content > 3.7 What Mastery Looks Like > 3.7.4 Adaptability & On-the-Fly Corrections', '["3-7-4-adaptability-on-the-fly-corrections","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-g-3-main-content-3-7-what-mastery-looks-like-3-7-4-adaptability-on-the-fly-corrections"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:55:44.833658+00', null), ('52690d25-392f-4470-a2de-dde61140fad2', '1e2052a5-ee5e-4421-83c1-cf4e7172cbf2', '8', '45', 'A successful Perazzi wood finish:

- **Visual Quality**  
  - Smooth, even surface with no runs, sags, or orange peel on visible areas.  
  - Pores filled or intentionally open in a **controlled, consistent** way.  
  - No dull patches (insufficient build or incomplete cure) or overly glossy patches (uneven pore filling).  
  - Color enriched but **natural**; grain and figure “pop” without looking artificially stained or plasticky.

- **Function & Durability**  
  - Finish resists sweat, rain, and daily handling; water beads on the surface.  
  - Checkering remains sharp and effective; no clogged diamonds.  
  - Finish can be maintained or repaired:  
    - Oil finishes: relatively easy local repair.  
    - Poly/film finishes: tougher but more challenging to spot-repair.

- **Tactile Feel**  
  - Stock feels **silky** and secure, not sticky or overly slick.  
