- Think of Part III as the **philosophy and result** of the processes in Part II.', null, '3.1.3 Step 3 – Part III: Cross-Cutting Systems', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part V: Learning Map for the Reader > 3. Main Content > 3.1 Recommended Reading Order & Strategy > 3.1.3 Step 3 – Part III: Cross-Cutting Systems', '["3-1-3-step-3-part-iii-cross-cutting-systems","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-v-learning-map-for-the-reader-3-main-content-3-1-recommended-reading-order-strategy-3-1-3-step-3-part-iii-cross-cutting-systems"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:58:59.884559+00', null), ('579a8d73-368f-401d-8dfa-4a4d79b91c96', '1e2052a5-ee5e-4421-83c1-cf4e7172cbf2', '17', '45', '- Finishing stock and fore-end **together** to maintain consistency.  
