- Guns imported or assembled outside official channels may:  
  - Lack warranty and factory support.  
  - Have unknown histories or questionable parts.  
- Very low prices on “new” Perazzis from unofficial sources are a red flag for grey-market or stolen guns.', null, '3.10.2 Grey-Market Guns and Import Channels', 'Perazzi Brand Bible – AI Reference > 3. Main Content > 3.10 Counterfeits, Grey Market, and Service Integrity > 3.10.2 Grey-Market Guns and Import Channels', '["3-10-2-grey-market-guns-and-import-channels","perazzi-brand-bible-ai-reference-3-main-content-3-10-counterfeits-grey-market-and-service-integrity-3-10-2-grey-market-guns-and-import-channels"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:51:07.263026+00', null), ('5db1423d-15d6-4409-a8c4-d6957dc01db1', 'c5b4fa4d-9f28-4908-a706-fbdc7cefdf94', '24', '53', '- Avoids **overfitting**, where constant tiny changes can erode shooter confidence.  
- Stops when:  
  - Fit is objectively within optimal ranges.  
  - Shooter is breaking targets well and expressing comfort.  
- Explains that further tiny tweaks may not yield improvement and can be revisited later if needed.', null, '3.4.5 When to Stop Adjusting', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.L > 3. Main Content > 3.4 Decisions & Trade-Offs > 3.4.5 When to Stop Adjusting', '["3-4-5-when-to-stop-adjusting","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-l-3-main-content-3-4-decisions-trade-offs-3-4-5-when-to-stop-adjusting"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:57:33.590816+00', null), ('5db93060-e8a0-40cd-80ba-667ce46878b5', '177a681e-a602-4d92-af07-b17c98816feb', '3', '13', '- **Definition:** The emotional stance and attitude expressed through Perazzi writing.  
- **Key attributes (all should be present in some form):**
