---', null, '0. Metadata', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.D > 0. Metadata', '["0-metadata","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-d-0-metadata"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:55:05.619789+00', null), ('5e4a9b94-3b18-4df3-bbaa-90989c59723a', 'e71c2213-11d3-4fbb-ad08-12dd9cb1fbe1', '33', '49', '- **Symptoms:**  
  - Patchy patterns with large holes; odd shapes (e.g., “donut” where center is thin and outer ring dense).

- **Potential Causes:**  
  - Barrel or choke issues (e.g., slight internal defect, burrs).  
  - Load-specific anomalies (wad behavior, shot quality).

- **Diagnosis & Remedies:**  
  - Re-test with the same load and a different load to distinguish ammo vs barrel issues.  
  - Inspect choke and bore; polish or correct any visible burrs.  
  - In rare cases, re-cut choke or replace barrel if patterns remain consistently poor.', null, '3.6.4 Irregular or Poor Patterns', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.K > 3. Main Content > 3.6 Failure Modes & Diagnosis > 3.6.4 Irregular or Poor Patterns', '["3-6-4-irregular-or-poor-patterns","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-k-3-main-content-3-6-failure-modes-diagnosis-3-6-4-irregular-or-poor-patterns"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:57:15.866317+00', null), ('5e558d01-6667-402e-87d5-b5c757d483d5', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '185', '238', 'Model name: MX2000S/3 | Base model: mx12-3 | Platform: MX | Category: competition | Disciplines: All Disciplines | Engraving Grade: 2000 | Combo configuration: no | Gauges: 12ga, 20ga | Barrel configuration style: over-under | Trigger: fixed | Trigger springs: coil | Rib: adjustable | Rib notches: 3-notch adjustable | Rib height: 8.0 mm | Rib style: notch', null, '### MX2000S/3', 'Models > MX2000S/3', '["model-details","mx2000s-3","platform:mx"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('5e9d7764-45de-40bc-88b1-979701328028', 'ea11bfa6-bea4-49fe-a9c8-e2f8d739eec6', '18', '38', '- **Lighter Hammers / Parts**  
  - Pros: faster lock time and potentially improved performance.  
  - Cons: risk of lighter primer strikes if not balanced with spring force; potentially more sensitive to fouling or friction.

- **Heavier, Robust Parts**  
  - Pros: extremely reliable ignition; long life.  
  - Cons: slightly longer lock time if not countered by stronger springs.

**Practical approach:**

- Work within Perazzi’s established design balance; any further skeletonizing or polishing for weight is done cautiously and with awareness of ignition reliability.

---', null, '3.4.6 Durability vs Extreme Lightness', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.D > 3. Main Content > 3.4 Decisions & Trade-Offs > 3.4.6 Durability vs Extreme Lightness', '["3-4-6-durability-vs-extreme-lightness","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-d-3-main-content-3-4-decisions-trade-offs-3-4-6-durability-vs-extreme-lightness"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:55:05.619789+00', null), ('5fd5d578-a148-420a-a126-66f9a4b02263', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '205', '238', 'Model name: MX410 SCO Gold Sideplates | Base model: mx410 | Platform: MX | Category: game | Disciplines: Game | Engraving Grade: SCO Gold Sideplates | Combo configuration: no | Gauges: 410ga | Barrel configuration style: over-under | Trigger: fixed | Trigger springs: coil | Rib: fixed', null, '### MX410 SCO Gold Sideplates', 'Models > MX410 SCO Gold Sideplates', '["model-details","mx410-sco-gold-sideplates","platform:mx"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('602f732a-fa60-4940-8227-5fe748a63d72', '1ae4b60f-6ad5-4475-9eb9-cabf6b0e829c', '28', '56', '- **Snap Caps & Dummy Shells**  
  - For trigger, ejection, and extraction tests.  
  - May include shells with spent or primed cases to inspect strike.

- **Trigger Pull Gauge**  
  - For measuring pull weight of each barrel’s trigger.

- **Headspace Gauges**  
  - GO/NO-GO gauges for each gauge/chamber length.

- **Firing Pin Protrusion Tools**  
  - Gauges or visual tools to check pin projection and rebound.

- **Balance & Weight Scale**  
  - For confirming total gun weight and, where needed, balance point.', null, '3.5.2 Functional Test Tools', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.J > 3. Main Content > 3.5 Tools & Measurements (Conceptual Level) > 3.5.2 Functional Test Tools', '["3-5-2-functional-test-tools","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-j-3-main-content-3-5-tools-measurements-conceptual-level-3-5-2-functional-test-tools"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:56:46.826724+00', null), ('60426d65-8e3b-468d-aee0-1dce456b7d17', 'a265cd6c-d21f-4b6d-a4d3-4aa569a508a9', '38', '58', '- Standard warranty: typically **two years** for the original owner on new guns.[113]
- Scope: manufacturing defects in materials or workmanship.  
- Exclusions: normal wear parts (springs, firing pins) and issues arising from third-party modifications.

---', null, '3.7.4 Warranty', 'Perazzi Brand Bible – AI Reference > 3. Main Content > 3.7 Parts, Accessories, and Service > 3.7.4 Warranty', '["3-7-4-warranty","perazzi-brand-bible-ai-reference-3-main-content-3-7-parts-accessories-and-service-3-7-4-warranty"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:51:07.263026+00', null), ('606faf6d-4a13-4a51-bb00-c5ef0fb4a049', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '198', '238', 'Model name: MX410 | Base model: mx410 | Platform: MX | Category: game | Disciplines: Game | Engraving Grade: SC2 | Combo configuration: no | Gauges: 410ga | Barrel configuration style: over-under | Trigger: fixed | Trigger springs: coil | Rib: fixed', null, '### MX410', 'Models > MX410', '["model-details","mx410","platform:mx"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('6083fd51-fee1-4c3f-a636-9d4cc56418a3', '1ae4b60f-6ad5-4475-9eb9-cabf6b0e829c', '23', '56', '- **More Lubricant**  
  - Pros: better protection during initial wear-in; reduces galling on high-pressure surfaces.  
  - Cons: attracts dirt and powder residue; can migrate into wood.

- **Minimal Lubricant**  
  - Pros: cleaner gun, less risk of oil soaking into wood.  
  - Cons: higher risk of early wear or galling if too dry.

**Practical approach:**  
- Use quality grease on **hinge pins, locking lugs, and cocking cams**.  
- Use light oil in **lockwork and triggers**.  
- Wipe off excess, leaving a controlled, thin film.', null, '3.4.3 Lubrication Amount & Type', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.J > 3. Main Content > 3.4 Decisions & Trade-Offs > 3.4.3 Lubrication Amount & Type', '["3-4-3-lubrication-amount-type","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-j-3-main-content-3-4-decisions-trade-offs-3-4-3-lubrication-amount-type"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:56:46.826724+00', null), ('60c24dca-9af6-4cb4-9cd3-b454f604b313', '67ca387d-48bc-4047-9404-209a02645c52', '0', '39', '- Source: Internal Perazzi USA Document - The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun
