- Polishing old guns requires extra care not to over-thin or erase markings.', null, '4.3 Refurbishment & Re-Bluing', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.H > 4. Edge Cases, Exceptions, and Caveats > 4.3 Refurbishment & Re-Bluing', '["4-3-refurbishment-re-bluing","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-h-4-edge-cases-exceptions-and-caveats-4-3-refurbishment-re-bluing"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:56:02.508279+00', null), ('676e2b03-4094-4c69-9582-b05aa1fabbad', 'afb5cf00-70cd-49aa-b1ee-096c29e9674e', '13', '26', '- See Perazzi as:
