- 30″ barrels with moderate choke constrictions, favoring Light Modified chokes across most situations[102].

She values the Perazzi’s weight distribution, which lets her move quickly onto targets without sacrificing stability. Fans may notice teal and pink accents on her Perazzi, reflecting her personality, but the underlying configuration is described as serious and performance-focused.

She has referred to her Perazzi shotgun as her “rock,” noting that it has seen her through many milestones and will carry her through more. The source frames her as a key figure in the future of women’s sporting clays and a strong ambassador of the Perazzi brand.

