  - Hairline crack visible around tang or stock head.  
  - Finish check that might indicate deeper issue.

- **Response:**  
  - Hold gun; have stockmaker assess.  
  - Repair (e.g., resin injection, pinning) if safe and invisible; re-finish affected area.  
  - Repeat test firing if crack indicated stress.  
  - If structural concern remains, re-stock and restart fit process.', null, '3.6.6 Stock Defects Emerging Late', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.M > 3. Main Content > 3.6 Failure Modes & Diagnosis > 3.6.6 Stock Defects Emerging Late', '["3-6-6-stock-defects-emerging-late","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-m-3-main-content-3-6-failure-modes-diagnosis-3-6-6-stock-defects-emerging-late"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:57:55.761534+00', null), ('72680ef0-b07b-409f-988c-f5b769a5ca5d', 'ea11bfa6-bea4-49fe-a9c8-e2f8d739eec6', '26', '38', '- Produces triggers that feel nearly identical across many guns of the same type.  
- Top shooters swapping between similar Perazzis often comment on how consistent the triggers feel; this is the cumulative result of master-level work.', null, '3.7.3 Repeatable Consistency Across Guns', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.D > 3. Main Content > 3.7 What Mastery Looks Like > 3.7.3 Repeatable Consistency Across Guns', '["3-7-3-repeatable-consistency-across-guns","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-d-3-main-content-3-7-what-mastery-looks-like-3-7-3-repeatable-consistency-across-guns"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:55:05.619789+00', null), ('727e325b-6281-44a4-be17-dc29131d5b10', '0894113c-c061-44ea-aa24-5dbe961f9a09', '9', '51', '- **Completed Checkered Surfaces**  
  - Grip and fore-end checkering cut to final depth and cleaned of dust and loose fibers.  
  - Patterns fully formed, with crisp, framed borders.

- **Stock & Fore-end Ready for Finishing**  
  - Checkering prepared for subsequent finishing processes:  
    - Some workflows may include a light sealer in checkering at this stage.  
    - In others, checkering is recut or cleaned after finish application to maintain sharp points.

- **Minor Repairs & Touch-Ups**  
  - Where small issues occurred (e.g., slight overruns, tiny chip-outs), masters may perform invisible touch-ups:  
    - Using checkering picks to restore diamond shape.  
    - Slightly modifying borders to absorb minor deviations.  
    - In limited cases, tiny fill-and-recut operations.

These outputs move on to **wood finishing** (and coordinated final passes of checkering if required by the process plan).

---', null, '3.2.2 Outputs', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.G > 3. Main Content > 3.2 Inputs & Outputs > 3.2.2 Outputs', '["3-2-2-outputs","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-g-3-main-content-3-2-inputs-outputs-3-2-2-outputs"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:55:44.833658+00', null), ('72f6d3f3-face-4243-b273-36152f5512b1', '67ca387d-48bc-4047-9404-209a02645c52', '32', '39', '- Throughout this handbook:
  - Statements are based on:
    - Published sources.
    - First-hand accounts (tour writeups, interviews).
    - Reasonable inference checked against known facts.
- Where information is not public:
  - We **explicitly avoid** making precise claims.
  - Instead, we:
    - Acknowledge the information gap.
    - Attribute performance to “Perazzi’s internal expertise” where appropriate.
- Examples of topics where we do **not** guess:
  - Exact hardness (HRC) of locking bolts.
  - Exact safety margins used in proof and over-proof.
  - Specific non-destructive testing protocols (e.g., X-ray, magnaflux).', null, '3.3.6 Respecting the Limits of Public Knowledge', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part IV: Perazzi vs General Gunmaking > 3. Main Content > 3.3 Unknowns & Respect for Proprietary Knowledge > 3.3.6 Respecting the Limits of Public Knowledge', '["3-3-6-respecting-the-limits-of-public-knowledge","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-iv-perazzi-vs-general-gunmaking-3-main-content-3-3-unknowns-respect-for-proprietary-knowledge-3-3-6-respecting-the-limits-of-public-knowledge"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:58:41.686758+00', null), ('7322dba0-8a85-4cbf-9d61-4a31b1623be7', '8078a4a0-2d04-41fd-bd01-ecfc4c710fbb', '44', '50', '### Alberto Fernández
