---', null, '3.3.8 Customer Perspective & Pride', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.M > 3. Main Content > 3.3 Core Knowledge & Skills > 3.3.8 Customer Perspective & Pride', '["3-3-8-customer-perspective-pride","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-m-3-main-content-3-3-core-knowledge-skills-3-3-8-customer-perspective-pride"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:57:55.761534+00', null), ('73ad473c-5013-4f2f-b5a2-9d45004d8251', '30dc5da6-b9ed-450e-8736-4a6dfce0983a', '6', '40', '- **Stress-Free Seating**  
  - Condition where the action sits in the stock without hidden pressure spots that could induce cracks.

- **Jar-Off / Interference**  
  - Potential for moving parts (triggers, safety, ejectors) to bind on wood, causing malfunctions; eliminated via careful relief and inletting.

- **Ergonomic Harmonization**  
  - Aligning dimensioned fit (LOP, drop, cast) with comfort and mount behavior, ensuring the gun “comes up naturally” for the shooter.

---', null, '2.5 Performance & Safety Concepts', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.F > 2. Key Concepts & Glossary > 2.5 Performance & Safety Concepts', '["2-5-performance-safety-concepts","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-f-2-key-concepts-glossary-2-5-performance-safety-concepts"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:55:32.068221+00', null), ('73c3ed1a-2099-4596-9adf-50f8470361fc', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '219', '238', 'Model name: MX8 SCO | Base model: mx8 | Platform: MX | Category: competition | Disciplines: Skeet, Sporting | Engraving Grade: SCO | Combo configuration: yes | Gauges: 12ga | Barrel configuration style: over-under | Trigger: removable | Trigger springs: flat, coil | Rib: fixed | Rib style: flat, step, ramp', null, '### MX8 SCO', 'Models > MX8 SCO', '["model-details","mx8-sco","platform:mx"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('73fc94ab-39bb-40c9-b05d-e39b2df04114', '053bd335-5ad7-49ba-a915-991f3ed97590', '6', '39', 'Quality at Perazzi is not an isolated department at the end of the line. It is:

