The overarching goal: each component and the assembled gun must meet **rigorous standards for dimensions, fit, and function**.', null, '3.1.1 QC as a Cross-Cutting Mindset', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part III: Cross-Cutting Systems > 3. Main Content > 3.1 Quality Control & Tolerances > 3.1.1 QC as a Cross-Cutting Mindset', '["3-1-1-qc-as-a-cross-cutting-mindset","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-iii-cross-cutting-systems-3-main-content-3-1-quality-control-tolerances-3-1-1-qc-as-a-cross-cutting-mindset"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:58:22.014078+00', null), ('74ee88c1-769b-4a0f-a50f-191496f461ac', '8078a4a0-2d04-41fd-bd01-ecfc4c710fbb', '47', '50', '### Gian Marco Berti
