no | Gauges: 16ga | Barrel configuration style: over-under | Trigger: fixed | Trigger springs: coil | Rib: fixed', null, '### MX16 SCO Sideplates', 'Models > MX16 SCO Sideplates', '["model-details","mx16-sco-sideplates","platform:mx"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('7c3491cc-c4ff-4fcf-a0bd-c2b53f4ae0b7', '536080f1-89e0-4124-9514-2ba022ce8a4b', '26', '36', '- Platforms like **The Champions Network** create a world where shooters can **live through the stories of others**.  
- Examples include following figures like **Wendell Cherry** and **David Radulovich** as they evolve alongside their guns.  
- The gun becomes a **central character** in these stories, embodying growth and transformation.', null, '3.6.2 Storytelling Immersion', 'Perazzi Brand Ethos & Personality – AI Reference > 3. Main Content > 3.6 The Perazzi Experience > 3.6.2 Storytelling Immersion', '["3-6-2-storytelling-immersion","perazzi-brand-ethos-personality-ai-reference-3-main-content-3-6-the-perazzi-experience-3-6-2-storytelling-immersion"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:51:25.853025+00', null), ('7c5462d8-d86b-4c75-b85a-d75ff4a66764', '6a033257-810e-408f-bcd1-5e0ba6cb7594', '10', '32', 'A product engineer at this station requires a blend of **ergonomics, ballistics, platform knowledge, and practical factory experience**.

Key domains:

- **Shotgun Ergonomics and Fit**  
  - Understanding how stock dimensions influence eye alignment, POI, felt recoil, and consistency of mount.  
  - Knowing how small changes in DAC, DAH, cast, and pitch manifest in live shooting.

- **Ballistics and Performance**  
  - Relationships between barrel length, weight distribution, swing dynamics, and recoil behavior.  
  - Impact of rib style, sighting plane, and choke system on pattern performance.

- **Perazzi Modular System Knowledge**  
  - Which barrels are compatible with which actions (e.g., MX and High Tech family interactions).[5]  
  - What fitting work is required when interchanging barrels or triggers.  
  - Limits on barrel profiles and chamber dimensions that preserve safe wall thickness and proof margins.

- **Discipline-Specific Experience**  
  - Differences in needs between trap, skeet, sporting clays, FITASC, live pigeon, and field shooting.  
  - Example: trap shooters may accept more front-heavy guns for stability; sporting clays shooters often prefer quicker acceleration.

- **Proof, Materials, and Safety**  
  - Knowledge of proof laws and Perazzi’s in-house proof practices.  
  - Familiarity with steels, heat treatment, and how barrel profiles affect safety and longevity.

- **Tacit and Historical Knowledge**  
  - Memory of past successful builds for high-level shooters.  
  - Intuitive sense of what combinations “work” or “feel wrong” even if they technically fit on paper.

- **Communication and Translation Skills**  
  - Ability to interpret customer language (e.g., “whippy gun,” “jumps too much”) into technical parameters.  
  - Ability to explain trade-offs and manage expectations about timelines, cost, and feasibility.

A master in this role mentally simulates how the gun will feel and perform **before** any physical part is made.

---', null, '3.3 Core Knowledge & Skills', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.A > 3. Main Content > 3.3 Core Knowledge & Skills', '["3-3-core-knowledge-skills","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-a-3-main-content-3-3-core-knowledge-skills"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:54:25.67313+00', null), ('7c6e8c27-0380-4073-abc4-06d97e3aeb5f', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '72', '238', 'Model name: High Tech S 2020 3 Palladium | Base model: high-tech-s-3 | Platform: HT | Category: competition | Disciplines: All Disciplines | Engraving Grade: 2020 Palladium | Combo configuration: no | Gauges: 12ga, 20ga | Barrel configuration style: over-under | Trigger: fixed | Trigger springs: coil | Rib: fixed | Rib style: flat, step, ramp', null, '### High Tech S 2020 3 Palladium', 'Models > High Tech S 2020 3 Palladium', '["model-details","high-tech-s-2020-3-palladium","platform:ht"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('7caaa664-38ac-4ffd-a5e6-4246fd9a2239', '00ee41e2-2a64-4498-9321-fde7e5df53f0', '4', '51', '- **Wood-to-Metal Fit**  
  - Joint quality between stock/fore-end and metal parts (action, trigger guard, fore-end iron).  
  - Checked for tightness, absence of gaps, and lack of proud or shy edges.

- **Surface Finish Quality**  
  - Overall condition of blued, case-colored, or coin-finished metal and oiled/varnished wood.  
  - Must be free of visible scratches, dents, overspray, or blemishes.

- **Checkering Quality**  
  - Checkered areas on grip and fore-end should have sharp diamonds and clean borders, with no fuzz, tear-out, or clogged finish.', null, '2.3 Fit & Finish Concepts', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.M > 2. Key Concepts & Glossary > 2.3 Fit & Finish Concepts', '["2-3-fit-finish-concepts","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-m-2-key-concepts-glossary-2-3-fit-finish-concepts"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:57:55.761534+00', null), ('7cd40068-b324-4285-9fcc-2afb73bd8801', '8078a4a0-2d04-41fd-bd01-ecfc4c710fbb', '16', '50', '### Diana Igaly
