- Adjusting pressure or number of passes in high/low spots to prevent over- or under-cutting.  
- Using visual cues (light reflections) and tactile feedback (sharp but not needle-like) to judge diamond quality.', null, '3.3.5 Uniform Depth & Diamond Quality', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.G > 3. Main Content > 3.3 Core Knowledge & Skills > 3.3.5 Uniform Depth & Diamond Quality', '["3-3-5-uniform-depth-diamond-quality","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-g-3-main-content-3-3-core-knowledge-skills-3-3-5-uniform-depth-diamond-quality"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:55:44.833658+00', null), ('83e3a80b-25eb-4cef-ac71-e0afa835d8f2', '00ee41e2-2a64-4498-9321-fde7e5df53f0', '2', '51', '- **Final Inspection, Proof Marks & Sign-Off Station (canonical)**  
