]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('870a2bf8-995c-408d-b647-72d6720d2da6', '500269f5-9624-4f5b-9ded-8de9740793b2', '4', '7', 'Modifications such as re-choking, porting, re-sleeving, back-boring, or barrel alterations performed by unauthorized third parties can affect the shotgun’s balance, performance, and safety. Such modifications will void the warranty and reduce the gun’s value.', null, 'Aftermarket Barrel Work', 'Consumer Warning Notice > Aftermarket Barrel Work', '["aftermarket-barrel-work","consumer-warning-notice-aftermarket-barrel-work"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:16.184829+00', null), ('877fc518-52f8-440d-9926-3a57e84b3801', 'dadad96d-904b-4c92-af84-aba4f15f7e85', '34', '48', '- Ability to scan a rack of blanks and quickly identify those best suited for a particular customer’s aesthetic and usage needs.  
- Recognizing subtle cues (color changes, grain shifts) that hint at potential sap pockets or weakness.  
- Knowing which regions’ walnut tends to be denser or softer and choosing accordingly for heavy-recoil vs lighter-duty guns.', null, '3.7.1 Intuition for Wood', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.E > 3. Main Content > 3.7 What Mastery Looks Like > 3.7.1 Intuition for Wood', '["3-7-1-intuition-for-wood","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-e-3-main-content-3-7-what-mastery-looks-like-3-7-1-intuition-for-wood"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:55:17.919795+00', null), ('87b6ab4c-ea7a-44c2-9a02-72b8245a1593', '00ee41e2-2a64-4498-9321-fde7e5df53f0', '42', '51', '- Masters can **coordinate quick rework** when needed, leveraging relationships with engravers, polishers, wood finishers, and assemblers for final touch‑ups without chaos.', null, '3.7.5 Coordination & Timing', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.M > 3. Main Content > 3.7 What Mastery Looks Like > 3.7.5 Coordination & Timing', '["3-7-5-coordination-timing","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-m-3-main-content-3-7-what-mastery-looks-like-3-7-5-coordination-timing"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:57:55.761534+00', null), ('87e09ea4-d970-46b3-8a2f-746926a8edfb', '1e2052a5-ee5e-4421-83c1-cf4e7172cbf2', '33', '45', '- Stock appears to **glow from within**, with figure shifting under light rather than being buried under a plastic-like film.  
- Pores are filled to the desired degree; finish is thin enough that wood still looks like wood.', null, '3.7.1 Depth & Chatoyance', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.I > 3. Main Content > 3.7 What Mastery Looks Like > 3.7.1 Depth & Chatoyance', '["3-7-1-depth-chatoyance","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-i-3-main-content-3-7-what-mastery-looks-like-3-7-1-depth-chatoyance"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:56:22.593132+00', null), ('87f80428-9015-42f9-9ebb-86edd7d9ce1c', 'fae85afb-4054-48f2-a2a6-8d756c851b62', '12', '32', '- **Goal**  
  Capture the customer’s exact requirements and define the technical design before manufacturing begins.

- **Inputs**  
  - Customer order details (measurements, chosen options, model type).  
  - Engineering standards (internal Perazzi design rules).  
  - Regulatory requirements (proof specifications, legal constraints).

- **Outputs**  
  - A **build sheet / blueprint** for the gun.  
  - Assigned **serial number**.  
  - CNC programming or tooling instructions tailored to this order.

- **Owned by**  
  Product engineer or master gunsmith (often in consultation with the customer or a dealer’s fitter).

