  - Drop-out trigger groups.
  - Bushed firing pins that are easily replaceable from the breech.
  - Replaceable locking bolts, made in **slightly oversized grades** for future tightening.
- Contrast with mid-grade guns:
  - Some use integral locking systems that require more invasive gunsmithing to tighten.
- Service philosophy:
  - Recognizes that serious competitors may shoot **hundreds of thousands of rounds**.
  - Availability of service kits and modular parts facilitates:
    - Routine maintenance.
    - Periodic overhauls without major re-machining.
- Peer comparison:
  - Some competitors (e.g., Krieghoff) share similar service-forward designs.
  - Many general makers assume much lower lifetime usage.', null, '3.1.8 Modular Serviceability', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part IV: Perazzi vs General Gunmaking > 3. Main Content > 3.1 Perazzi-Specific Practices and Innovations > 3.1.8 Modular Serviceability', '["3-1-8-modular-serviceability","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-iv-perazzi-vs-general-gunmaking-3-main-content-3-1-perazzi-specific-practices-and-innovations-3-1-8-modular-serviceability"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:58:41.686758+00', null), ('8f7eeb67-a1cb-461f-acf4-b2817e783e49', '70499c1f-6a48-44b7-804a-fc63b2ea9317', '12', '35', 'Even with highly automated CNC, **judgment** plays a central role. Key recurring trade-offs include:', null, '3.4 Decisions & Trade-Offs', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.B > 3. Main Content > 3.4 Decisions & Trade-Offs', '["3-4-decisions-trade-offs","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-b-3-main-content-3-4-decisions-trade-offs"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:54:34.806094+00', null), ('8f8ee53f-a801-43eb-bb09-7575b682f9cd', 'c5b4fa4d-9f28-4908-a706-fbdc7cefdf94', '15', '53', '- Adjusts **trigger shoe position** so the shooter’s finger pad lands naturally on the trigger.  
