Annabelle is also presented as an advocate for women in shooting sports, sharing her story in media and encouraging increased female participation. She became a certified instructor in her early 20s, teaching women and youth.

The source describes her competitive demeanor as focused and composed, even under historic pressure. Her sixth ladies national title in 2020 is described as “unprecedented,” cementing her as one of the greatest female sporting clays shooters in U.S. history[96]. She is quoted as “never satisfied with the status quo, always seeking new opportunities to explore”[101].', null, '3.2.5.1 Biography & Background', 'Perazzi USA Team & Supported Shooters (AI-Optimized Reference) > 3. Main Content > 3.2 Supported Shooters > 3.2.5 Annabelle Ayres – Sporting Clays (Supported Shooter) > 3.2.5.1 Biography & Background', '["3-2-5-1-biography-background","perazzi-usa-team-supported-shooters-ai-optimized-reference-3-main-content-3-2-supported-shooters-3-2-5-annabelle-ayres-sporting-clays-supported-shooter-3-2-5-1-biography-background"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:51:56.586148+00', null), ('918760d5-a898-458c-8a24-9815565be29f', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '75', '238', 'Model name: High Tech S 2020 5 Palladium | Base model: high-tech-s | Platform: HT | Category: competition | Disciplines: All Disciplines | Engraving Grade: 2020 Palladium | Combo configuration: no | Gauges: 12ga, 20ga | Barrel configuration style: over-under | Trigger: fixed | Trigger springs: coil | Rib: fixed | Rib style: flat, step, ramp', null, '### High Tech S 2020 5 Palladium', 'Models > High Tech S 2020 5 Palladium', '["model-details","high-tech-s-2020-5-palladium","platform:ht"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('919db171-0f83-4d22-b613-6be8cd8135cf', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '113', '238', 'Model name: High Tech S X Gold | Base model: high-tech-s | Platform: HT | Category: competition | Disciplines: All Disciplines | Engraving Grade: X Gold | Combo configuration: no | Gauges: 12ga, 20ga | Barrel configuration style: over-under | Trigger: fixed | Trigger springs: coil | Rib: fixed | Rib style: flat, step, ramp', null, '### High Tech S X Gold', 'Models > High Tech S X Gold', '["model-details","high-tech-s-x-gold","platform:ht"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('91acc6d4-f8db-43b2-8027-c4b81f5416c6', '536080f1-89e0-4124-9514-2ba022ce8a4b', '19', '36', '- See the gun as a **marker of having "arrived"** in their journey.  
- Intend to treat the gun as a **generational artifact** — something to be passed down.  
- Respond strongly to narratives about legacy, inheritance, and long-term significance.', null, '3.4.3 Achievers & Legacy Builders', 'Perazzi Brand Ethos & Personality – AI Reference > 3. Main Content > 3.4 Audience Connection > 3.4.3 Achievers & Legacy Builders', '["3-4-3-achievers-legacy-builders","perazzi-brand-ethos-personality-ai-reference-3-main-content-3-4-audience-connection-3-4-3-achievers-legacy-builders"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:51:25.853025+00', null), ('91fe21c4-bf4b-4878-8c6e-20d92cf62d1b', '1e2052a5-ee5e-4421-83c1-cf4e7172cbf2', '27', '45', '- Sandpapers (320–600+ grit) on blocks and flexible backers.  
- Steel wool (0000) or non-woven abrasive pads.  
- Tack cloths and compressed air for dust removal.', null, '3.5.1 Surface Preparation Tools', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.I > 3. Main Content > 3.5 Tools & Measurements (Conceptual Level) > 3.5.1 Surface Preparation Tools', '["3-5-1-surface-preparation-tools","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-i-3-main-content-3-5-tools-measurements-conceptual-level-3-5-1-surface-preparation-tools"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:56:22.593132+00', null), ('9227e57c-db46-4281-a295-f2d116338c62', '30dc5da6-b9ed-450e-8736-4a6dfce0983a', '4', '40', '- **Stock Head**  
  - Region of wood that surrounds and supports the action’s rear, including inletting for tangs and draw bolt.

- **Wrist**  
  - Narrow section behind the action; structurally critical and susceptible to cracking if grain or inletting is poor.

- **Fore-end Iron & Latch**  
  - Metal framework and latch mechanism that attach fore-end to barrels and action.

- **Through-Bolt / Draw Bolt**  
  - Bolt that runs through stock to secure it to action; requires accurately positioned and aligned hole and inletting.', null, '2.3 Wood & Component Concepts', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.F > 2. Key Concepts & Glossary > 2.3 Wood & Component Concepts', '["2-3-wood-component-concepts","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-f-2-key-concepts-glossary-2-3-wood-component-concepts"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:55:32.068221+00', null), ('927213ec-96ee-4478-b738-3bed609dad6f', '1ae4b60f-6ad5-4475-9eb9-cabf6b0e829c', '18', '56', '- Tighten stock bolt enough to ensure secure contact between stock head and action, but not so much as to crush fibers or induce cracks.  
- Understand how over-tightening can cause long-term stock head failures and how under-tightening leads to movement and looseness.', null, '3.3.7 Stock Bolt Torque & Wood Protection', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.J > 3. Main Content > 3.3 Core Knowledge & Skills > 3.3.7 Stock Bolt Torque & Wood Protection', '["3-3-7-stock-bolt-torque-wood-protection","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-j-3-main-content-3-3-core-knowledge-skills-3-3-7-stock-bolt-torque-wood-protection"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:56:46.826724+00', null), ('92ad23e2-d927-440f-94de-5104f7b2c934', 'c5b4fa4d-9f28-4908-a706-fbdc7cefdf94', '17', '53', '- Identifies subtle discomfort sources:  
  - Sharp comb edges against cheek.  
  - Excessive palm swell, or grip too full/small.  
- Performs **micro‑shaping** (small sanding and re‑oiling) on limited areas when this yields significant comfort gains without major re-checkering or refinishing.  
- Suggests non‑invasive options such as leather comb covers when more dramatic carving is not appropriate at this stage.', null, '3.3.7 Fine Ergonomics & Comfort Adjustments', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.L > 3. Main Content > 3.3 Core Knowledge & Skills > 3.3.7 Fine Ergonomics & Comfort Adjustments', '["3-3-7-fine-ergonomics-comfort-adjustments","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-l-3-main-content-3-3-core-knowledge-skills-3-3-7-fine-ergonomics-comfort-adjustments"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:57:33.590816+00', null), ('92b0c21c-e235-4b86-ae31-e5bd556f6de2', '8078a4a0-2d04-41fd-bd01-ecfc4c710fbb', '29', '50', '### Giovanni Cernogoraz
**Country:** Croatia
**Event:** Men’s Trap
**Medal:** Gold
**Olympics:** 2012 London
**Perazzi platform:** MX2000/8
**Highlights:** Cernogoraz won trap gold at London 2012 in a thrilling shoot-off, using a Perazzi MX2000/8:contentReference[oaicite:101]{index=101}. His victory was Croatia’s first shooting gold. Notably, all three men’s trap medalists in 2012 used Perazzis – a podium sweep for the brand:contentReference[oaicite:102]{index=102}. Cernogoraz’s calm finish and praise for his gun (“it never let me down in the shoot-off”) highlighted Perazzi’s role.
**Sources:**
- Wikipedia – Olympic use (Perazzi):contentReference[oaicite:103]{index=103}
- Rock Island Auction – 2008/2012 all-medalist Perazzi fact:contentReference[oaicite:104]{index=104}', null, '### Giovanni Cernogoraz', 'Olympic Medals > Giovanni Cernogoraz', '["olympic-medals","giovanni-cernogoraz"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Loyalist","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:20.792823+00', null), ('933cf969-7766-440b-abcc-3caf9611092e', '8078a4a0-2d04-41fd-bd01-ecfc4c710fbb', '8', '50', '### Michael Diamond
