1. **Removable Trigger Group**[3]  
   - The complete trigger and lockwork assembly can be dropped out of the receiver as a unit.  
   - Benefits:
     - Easy maintenance and service.
     - Allows competitors to carry a **spare trigger group** at major events.
     - Facilitates specialized tuning of trigger pull and lock time.

2. **Low-Profile Action with Modified Boss-Style Locking**[4]  
   - Low action height keeps the barrels closer to the shooter’s hands and shoulder.  
   - Modified Boss-style locking system provides:
     - Strong engagement between monobloc and receiver.
     - Long-term durability under heavy use.
     - A compact, elegant profile that feels lively yet solid.

3. **Monobloc Barrel Construction**  
   - Each barrel set is built from:
     - A **machined monobloc** containing the two chambers and locking lugs.
     - Two **barrel tubes** inserted and fixed into the monobloc.  
   - Advantages:
     - Structural strength and consistency.
     - Simplified barrel **regulation** (aligning point-of-impact between barrels).
     - Efficient, repeatable fabrication for custom configurations.

4. **Competition-Oriented Weight and Balance**  
   - Perazzi shotguns are intentionally **slightly heavier** than delicate English field guns.  
   - Priorities:
     - Recoil mitigation during extended training and competition.
     - Smooth, controlled swing for clay targets.
     - **Pattern consistency** shot after shot.

Overall, the architecture embodies **engineering robustness** paired with **fine hand-fitted craft**.', null, '3.2.1 Architectural Hallmarks of Perazzi O/U Shotguns', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part I: Product & System Overview > 3. Main Content > 3.2 Architectural Hallmarks and Brand Positioning > 3.2.1 Architectural Hallmarks of Perazzi O/U Shotguns', '["3-2-1-architectural-hallmarks-of-perazzi-o-u-shotguns","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-i-product-system-overview-3-main-content-3-2-architectural-hallmarks-and-brand-positioning-3-2-1-architectural-hallmarks-of-perazzi-o-u-shotguns"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:54:11.853745+00', null), ('99098e2f-f492-4008-9772-76c846ae1e68', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '8', '238', 'Model name: DC SCO Gold Sideplates | Base model: dc | Platform: DC | Category: mixed | Disciplines: Sporting, Game | Engraving Grade: SCO Gold Sideplates | Combo configuration: no | Gauges: 12ga, 20ga | Barrel configuration style: side-by-side | Trigger: removable | Trigger springs: flat, coil | Rib: fixed | Rib style: flat, step, ramp', null, '### DC SCO Gold Sideplates', 'Models > DC SCO Gold Sideplates', '["model-details","dc-sco-gold-sideplates","platform:dc"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('996b1038-4aa3-4a93-aeb8-a810461ad466', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '30', '238', 'Model name: High Tech 2020/10 | Base model: high-tech-10 | Platform: HT | Category: competition | Disciplines: Trap | Engraving Grade: 2020 | Combo configuration: yes | Gauges: 12ga | Barrel configuration style: top-single | Trigger: removable | Trigger springs: flat, coil | Rib: adjustable | Rib notches: 4-notch adjustable | Rib height: 17.0 mm | Rib style: notch', null, '### High Tech 2020/10', 'Models > High Tech 2020/10', '["model-details","high-tech-2020-10","platform:ht"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('9986cb1c-0584-4548-91d9-d6bae8c1e17b', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '144', '238', 'Model name: MX12 SC3 Gold Sideplates | Base model: mx12 | Platform: MX | Category: mixed | Disciplines: Sporting, Game | Engraving Grade: SC3 Gold Sideplates | Combo configuration: no | Gauges: 12ga | Barrel configuration style: over-under | Trigger: fixed | Trigger springs: coil | Rib: fixed | Rib style: flat, step, ramp', null, '### MX12 SC3 Gold Sideplates', 'Models > MX12 SC3 Gold Sideplates', '["model-details","mx12-sc3-gold-sideplates","platform:mx"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('998c7c83-4798-4a4c-9af3-3ad124646b13', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '236', '238', 'Model name: High Tech Skeet | Base model: high-tech | Platform: HT | Category: competition | Disciplines: Skeet | Engraving Grade: Standard | Combo configuration: no | Gauges: 12ga, 20ga | Barrel configuration style: over-under | Trigger: removable | Trigger springs: flat, coil | Rib: fixed | Rib style: flat', null, '### High Tech Skeet', 'Models > High Tech Skeet', '["model-details","high-tech-skeet","platform:ht"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('99e67752-06e8-425b-93a3-c33ec2e06c85', '053bd335-5ad7-49ba-a915-991f3ed97590', '12', '39', 'QC is not purely mechanical; cosmetics are also scrutinized:

- **Bluing**
  - Checked under strong light for:
    - Uniform color.
    - Even polish.
    - No thin spots (e.g., around ribs, joints).
- **Wood finish**
  - Inspected for:
    - Dust nibs.
    - Cloudy or uneven areas.
    - Poorly filled pores.
- **Checkering**
  - Examined (sometimes with magnification) to ensure:
    - Sharp points.
    - Clean lines without run-overs.
- **Engraving**
  - Verified against approved patterns for:
    - Completeness.
    - Absence of slips or rough transitions.
  - Signature of the engraver (on higher grades) is itself a quality mark, followed by factory inspection.', null, '3.1.7 Cosmetic QC', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part III: Cross-Cutting Systems > 3. Main Content > 3.1 Quality Control & Tolerances > 3.1.7 Cosmetic QC', '["3-1-7-cosmetic-qc","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-iii-cross-cutting-systems-3-main-content-3-1-quality-control-tolerances-3-1-7-cosmetic-qc"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:58:22.014078+00', null), ('9a3a2d6d-71d7-4ae0-8e8d-6aacc1b8d3ca', '82a899f9-2019-4029-b599-221316624acd', '9', '38', 'Ian Lawrence is portrayed as a young but highly accomplished face in American Trap. Hailing from Illinois, Ian fell in love with trapshooting at just 10 years old and devoted himself to the sport[10].

Early achievements:

- At 13, he swept his Sub-Junior division at the Grand American, shooting a perfect 100/100 and winning three events (including the President’s Handicap) against fields of over a thousand competitors[11][12].  
- This period is described as revealing a rising prodigy.

Ian is characterized by an earnest, authentic demeanor, balancing quiet confidence with relentless practice – summarized in the source as “practice, practice, practice” until he learned how to “focus and break ’em all”[13].

By his early twenties, Ian had established himself among trapshooting’s elite:

- 9-time ATA All-American team honoree.  
- The 499th person ever to complete the ATA Grand Slam (breaking 200 straight singles, 100 straight doubles, and 100 straight from 27 yards)[14].  
- In 2025, he captured the High-Over-All title at the ATA U.S. Open, posting top scores in both doubles and overall HOA[15].  
- At the Missouri State shoot, he swept non-resident Doubles, HAA, and HOA championships[15].

The source emphasizes that Ian’s consistency across all trap disciplines reflects a maturity beyond his years and describes his career trajectory as “meteoric.”', null, '3.1.2.1 Biography & Background', 'Perazzi USA Team & Supported Shooters (AI-Optimized Reference) > 3. Main Content > 3.1 Sponsored Shooters (Perazzi USA Team) > 3.1.2 Ian Lawrence – American Trap (Sponsored Shooter) > 3.1.2.1 Biography & Background', '["3-1-2-1-biography-background","perazzi-usa-team-supported-shooters-ai-optimized-reference-3-main-content-3-1-sponsored-shooters-perazzi-usa-team-3-1-2-ian-lawrence-american-trap-sponsored-shooter-3-1-2-1-biography-background"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:51:56.586148+00', null), ('9a8502f0-6bea-4afb-adea-0e6eb5cb8688', '30dc5da6-b9ed-450e-8736-4a6dfce0983a', '18', '40', '- **Thin, Elegant Wrist & Grip**  
  - Pros: aesthetically pleasing; can feel nimble in hand.  
  - Cons: increased risk of weakness in the wrist, especially for heavy-recoil guns.

- **Slightly Fuller, Stronger Sections**  
  - Pros: more wood around tangs and wrist; greater durability.  
  - Cons: can appear bulkier; may feel less refined.

**Practical approach:**

- Balance aesthetics and strength:  
  - Leave extra “hidden” strength under the surface where possible, especially for heavy recoil usage.  
  - Accept slightly fuller dimensions if required for long-term durability.', null, '3.4.2 Strength vs Elegance (Thickness & Contour)', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.F > 3. Main Content > 3.4 Decisions & Trade-Offs > 3.4.2 Strength vs Elegance (Thickness & Contour)', '["3-4-2-strength-vs-elegance-thickness-contour","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-f-3-main-content-3-4-decisions-trade-offs-3-4-2-strength-vs-elegance-thickness-contour"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:55:32.068221+00', null), ('9abf0378-e401-459f-89d8-b1ed720ac513', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '13', '238', 'Model name: High Tech | Base model: high-tech | Platform: HT | Category: competition | Disciplines: All Disciplines | Engraving Grade: Standard | Combo configuration: no | Gauges: 12ga, 20ga | Barrel configuration style: over-under | Trigger: removable | Trigger springs: flat, coil | Rib: fixed | Rib style: flat, step, ramp', null, '### High Tech', 'Models > High Tech', '["model-details","high-tech","platform:ht"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('9b8e3273-c59f-4fc9-b343-91227de5b297', '30dc5da6-b9ed-450e-8736-4a6dfce0983a', '39', '40', '- **1. High-Level Overview** – Scope and purpose of the Stock Inletting & Final Shaping station.  
