---', null, '3.5.4 Safety & Record-Keeping', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.K > 3. Main Content > 3.5 Tools & Measurements (Conceptual Level) > 3.5.4 Safety & Record-Keeping', '["3-5-4-safety-record-keeping","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-k-3-main-content-3-5-tools-measurements-conceptual-level-3-5-4-safety-record-keeping"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:57:15.866317+00', null), ('a2a5aa9d-37a9-40ec-b28f-e06be4c60373', 'afb5cf00-70cd-49aa-b1ee-096c29e9674e', '19', '26', '- Emphasize:
