- One side: **High Technology** (CNC, modern metrology, contemporary finishes).  
- Other side: **Traditional Craft** (hand-fitting, engraving, checkering, artistry).

Perazzi exemplifies the balance:

- Machine cuts → human fits.  
- Machine roughs → human finishes.  
- Machine drills barrel → human straightens and regulates.  
- Machine shapes stock → human refines, checkers, and finishes.

This model helps you predict, in any given station, **what is likely CNC vs handwork** – and why.', null, '3.3.4 Craft vs Machine Balance', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part V: Learning Map for the Reader > 3. Main Content > 3.3 Mental Models & Diagrams > 3.3.4 Craft vs Machine Balance', '["3-3-4-craft-vs-machine-balance","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-v-learning-map-for-the-reader-3-main-content-3-3-mental-models-diagrams-3-3-4-craft-vs-machine-balance"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:58:59.884559+00', null), ('a35db7bd-2b65-4f6c-b22e-79376898aec5', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '71', '238', 'Model name: High Tech S 2020 3 Gold | Base model: high-tech-s-3 | Platform: HT | Category: competition | Disciplines: All Disciplines | Engraving Grade: 2020 Gold | Combo configuration: no | Gauges: 12ga, 20ga | Barrel configuration style: over-under | Trigger: fixed | Trigger springs: coil | Rib: adjustable | Rib notches: 3-notch adjustable | Rib height: 8.0 mm | Rib style: notch', null, '### High Tech S 2020 3 Gold', 'Models > High Tech S 2020 3 Gold', '["model-details","high-tech-s-2020-3-gold","platform:ht"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('a3600fed-7ccd-4665-bf6c-1500cd7f2d81', '536080f1-89e0-4124-9514-2ba022ce8a4b', '28', '36', 'This section collects **canonical phrasing** that reflects the brand’s ethos and should guide future copy generation.', null, '3.7 Signature Language Patterns', 'Perazzi Brand Ethos & Personality – AI Reference > 3. Main Content > 3.7 Signature Language Patterns', '["3-7-signature-language-patterns","perazzi-brand-ethos-personality-ai-reference-3-main-content-3-7-signature-language-patterns"]', '["Prospect","Own