- Often takes targets early with a rhythmic cadence built over thousands of hours of practice.  
- Credits fundamentals and faith with contributing to both academic success and shooting achievements[93].  
- Known for modesty and sportsmanship, quick to congratulate competitors and support friends.  
- Balances professional life with ongoing competition and has begun coaching juniors.', null, '3.2.7.1 Biography & Background', 'Perazzi USA Team & Supported Shooters (AI-Optimized Reference) > 3. Main Content > 3.2 Supported Shooters > 3.2.7 Josh Poole – American Skeet (Supported Shooter) > 3.2.7.1 Biography & Background', '["3-2-7-1-biography-background","perazzi-usa-team-supported-shooters-ai-optimized-reference-3-main-content-3-2-supported-shooters-3-2-7-josh-poole-american-skeet-supported-shooter-3-2-7-1-biography-background"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:51:56.586148+00', null), ('ae229aa8-9f60-4e6a-b9ff-59db06bc4529', 'ea11bfa6-bea4-49fe-a9c8-e2f8d739eec6', '21', '38', '- **Trigger Pull Weight**  
  - Measured repeatedly for consistency across both barrels.

- **Sear Engagement**  
  - Depth/overlap of sear and hammer notch, sometimes judged visually and by contact pattern (soot/marking compound), rather than in explicit millimeter values.

- **Safety Engagement**  
