  - **Sporting / Field / Driven Game**: may require quicker handling and different regulation priorities.', null, '2.5 Regulation & Use-Case Concepts', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.C > 2. Key Concepts & Glossary > 2.5 Regulation & Use-Case Concepts', '["2-5-regulation-use-case-concepts","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-c-2-key-concepts-glossary-2-5-regulation-use-case-concepts"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:54:47.674361+00', null), ('b103431f-0f3b-4fdd-b465-c1dfa5be575b', '00ee41e2-2a64-4498-9321-fde7e5df53f0', '10', '51', '- **Approved, Packaged Gun**  
