- Key functions for users:
  - Find service centers and contact information.
  - Understand what can be done at the owner level vs. what must go to professionals.', null, '3.3.6 Service & Support – Ownership Backbone', 'PerazziGPT v2 – Source Corpus Manifest (User-Facing Site Overview) > 3. Core Experiences & Main Site Areas > 3.3 How the Main Site Areas Work > 3.3.6 Service & Support – Ownership Backbone', '["3-3-6-service-support-ownership-backbone","perazzigpt-v2-source-corpus-manifest-user-facing-site-overview-3-core-experiences-main-site-areas-3-3-how-the-main-site-areas-work-3-3-6-service-support-ownership-backbone"]', '["Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:59:09.736657+00', null), ('b7d20db7-80f1-4d9d-8324-ba85b5a2eae4', 'a265cd6c-d21f-4b6d-a4d3-4aa569a508a9', '26', '58', '- Perazzi claims **62 Olympic medals at 11 Olympics** through 2021, including at least **14 gold medals** in trap and skeet events.[15]
