There are no formal caliper-based measurements for spacing; the **tool’s LPI and layout** serve as the primary regulators.

---', null, '3.5.4 Informal “Measurements”', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.G > 3. Main Content > 3.5 Tools & Measurements (Conceptual Level) > 3.5.4 Informal “Measurements”', '["3-5-4-informal-measurements","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-g-3-main-content-3-5-tools-measurements-conceptual-level-3-5-4-informal-measurements"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:55:44.833658+00', null), ('b9c62f61-256f-45ee-99da-6f8314bc3a43', '6a033257-810e-408f-bcd1-5e0ba6cb7594', '28', '32', '- Market-specific markings (e.g., import requirements).  
- Discipline-specific rules:  
