  - No doubling.
  - Reliable manual safety operation.
  - Resistance to jar-off from shocks or drops.', null, '3.1.1 Purpose', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.D > 3. Main Content > 3.1 Station Purpose & Success Criteria > 3.1.1 Purpose', '["3-1-1-purpose","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-d-3-main-content-3-1-station-purpose-success-criteria-3-1-1-purpose"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:55:05.619789+00', null), ('ba74e9ce-5ce9-4885-940b-f1c38187b8ec', '8078a4a0-2d04-41fd-bd01-ecfc4c710fbb', '28', '50', '### Peter Wilson
