- **Geographic and date context:**  
  All dates, titles, and geographic references are taken directly from the source. No attempt has been made to verify or update them beyond what is written.', null, '4. Edge Cases, Exceptions, and Caveats', 'Perazzi USA Team & Supported Shooters (AI-Optimized Reference) > 4. Edge Cases, Exceptions, and Caveats', '["4-edge-cases-exceptions-and-caveats","perazzi-usa-team-supported-shooters-ai-optimized-reference-4-edge-cases-exceptions-and-caveats"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:51:56.586148+00', null), ('bdbd6f47-f13b-4f5c-91b6-781d45873915', '4ae532ea-bef9-47fe-9bd9-051858902e2f', '11', '23', '- Use this **Learning Map** not only at the start but as a recurring checklist:
