- Avoiding any oversize internal cuts that would compromise later hand fit.', null, '3.3.8 Joinery & Inletting Awareness', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.E > 3. Main Content > 3.3 Core Knowledge & Skills > 3.3.8 Joinery & Inletting Awareness', '["3-3-8-joinery-inletting-awareness","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-e-3-main-content-3-3-core-knowledge-skills-3-3-8-joinery-inletting-awareness"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:55:17.919795+00', null), ('c249e12b-8e52-4802-8645-6c89e116e7a5', 'a265cd6c-d21f-4b6d-a4d3-4aa569a508a9', '35', '58', '- Perazzi publishes detailed **parts schematics and lists** for actions, triggers, ejectors, and other assemblies.[98][99]
