  - May suggest changes in recoil pad or shooter setup rather than structural gun changes.', null, '3.6.6 Excessive Recoil or Poor Balance (Subjective)', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.K > 3. Main Content > 3.6 Failure Modes & Diagnosis > 3.6.6 Excessive Recoil or Poor Balance (Subjective)', '["3-6-6-excessive-recoil-or-poor-balance-subjective","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-k-3-main-content-3-6-failure-modes-diagnosis-3-6-6-excessive-recoil-or-poor-balance-subjective"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:57:15.866317+00', null), ('c796fc50-4bbb-4bf5-b129-ec784692e8fb', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '45', '238', 'Model name: High Tech 5 SC3 Gold | Base model: high-tech-5 | Platform: HT | Category: competition | Disciplines: All Disciplines | Engraving Grade: SC3 Gold | Combo configuration: no | Gauges: 12ga, 20ga | Barrel configuration style: over-under | Trigger: removable | Trigger springs: flat, coil | Rib: adjustable | Rib notches: 5-notch adjustable | Rib height: 24.0 mm | Rib style: notch', null, '### High Tech 5 SC3 Gold', 'Models > High Tech 5 SC3 Gold', '["model-details","high-tech-5-sc3-gold","platform:ht"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('c79e2e83-b5a5-452b-9663-06eb75b5de07', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '99', '238', 'Model name: High Tech S P 3 | Base model: high-tech-s-3 | Platform: HT | Category: competition | Disciplines: All Disciplines | Engraving Grade: P | Combo configuration: no | Gauges: 12ga, 20ga | Barrel configuration style: over-under | Trigger: fixed | Trigger springs: coil | Rib: adjustable | Rib notches: 3-notch adjustable | Rib height: 8.0 mm | Rib style: notch', null, '### High Tech S P 3', 'Models > High Tech S P 3', '["model-details","high-tech-s-p-3","platform:ht"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('c7a0f6eb-0129-41e5-bbcb-e9996b96c829', 'f8b0315e-200b-46a7-afda-d38cc89aff71', '2', '39', '- **Barrel Fabrication & Regulation Station (canonical)**  
  - Synonyms: *Barrel Shop*, *Barrel Department*, *Barrel Making & Regulation*.  
  - Definition: The station where barrel tubes are drilled, reamed, straightened, joined to a monobloc and ribs, choked, and regulated so both barrels shoot to the intended point of impact.

- **Barrel Maker / Barrel Smith (canonical)**  
  - Synonyms: *Barrel Specialist*, *Regulator*.  
  - Definition: Craftsperson responsible for executing and overseeing the processes in this station.', null, '2.1 Roles and Station', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.C > 2. Key Concepts & Glossary > 2.1 Roles and Station', '["2-1-roles-and-station","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-c-2-key-concepts-glossary-2-1-roles-and-station"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:54:47.674361+00', null), ('c7b2a836-f6bc-4633-95f2-59524dff41bf', '5eba6cac-e507-407b-80c3-b76bdb3f3e89', '21', '32', 'Typical flow:

