**Caveat:** The barrel maker must verify that custom dimensions remain within safety limits and proof rules.', null, '4.3 Special Chamber and Forcing Cone Specifications', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.C > 4. Edge Cases, Exceptions, and Caveats > 4.3 Special Chamber and Forcing Cone Specifications', '["4-3-special-chamber-and-forcing-cone-specifications","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-c-4-edge-cases-exceptions-and-caveats-4-3-special-chamber-and-forcing-cone-specifications"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:54:47.674361+00', null), ('c8647e3b-52e9-4c03-9004-4ef54dfc4550', '0894113c-c061-44ea-aa24-5dbe961f9a09', '21', '51', '- **Borders (single or double)**  
  - Pros: cleanly frames pattern; helps hide minor end-of-line irregularities.  
  - Cons: requires additional precision and time.

- **Borderless / Fade-Out Patterns**  
