**Country:** Great Britain
**Event:** Men’s Trap
**Medal:** Bronze
**Olympics:** 2016 Rio de Janeiro
**Perazzi platform:** MX2000/3
**Highlights:** Ling captured trap bronze at Rio 2016 with a Perazzi MX2000/3:contentReference[oaicite:148]{index=148}. In a rainy final, his equipment functioned flawlessly. Ling’s medal – Britain’s first Olympic trap medal in decades – came after years of using Perazzi guns in training. His MX2000/3, a model with backbored barrels for reduced recoil, helped him endure the grueling 5-round qualification and a tense final to finally stand on the podium:contentReference[oaicite:149]{index=149}.
**Sources:**
- Wikipedia – Olympic use (Perazzi):contentReference[oaicite:150]{index=150}
- BBC Sport – Rio 2016 trap bronze story (notes Ling’s Perazzi):contentReference[oaicite:151]{index=151}', null, '### Edward Ling', 'Olympic Medals > Edward Ling', '["olympic-medals","edward-ling"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Loyalist","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:20.792823+00', null), ('d1629ac3-b2f0-4b74-8539-74419dc3f09e', '70499c1f-6a48-44b7-804a-fc63b2ea9317', '24', '35', '- Evaluates not only dimensions but also **visual flow** of the action: symmetry of fences, graceful transitions between surfaces, and how the receiver will look when engraved.  
- Lightly polishes and blends key contours so that later engraving and finishing complement the geometry.', null, '3.7.2 Artistic Eye and Symmetry', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.B > 3. Main Content > 3.7 What Mastery Looks Like > 3.7.2 Artistic Eye and Symmetry', '["3-7-2-artistic-eye-and-symmetry","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-b-3-main-content-3-7-what-mastery-looks-like-3-7-2-artistic-eye-and-symmetry"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:54:34.806094+00', null), ('d22c9385-c4b1-4e28-b65c-5357f8295fbe', '536080f1-89e0-4124-9514-2ba022ce8a4b', '5', '36', '- **Loyalists**  
  Lifelong shooters who view Perazzi as a badge of authenticity and legacy.

- **Prestige Buyers**  
  Customers seeking aspirational excellence and emotional validation through exclusivity.

- **Achievers & Legacy Builders**  
  Individuals who see a Perazzi as a mark of having "arrived" and as a generational artifact meant to be passed down.', null, '2.4 Audience Segments', 'Perazzi Brand Ethos & Personality – AI Reference > 2. Key Concepts & Glossary > 2.4 Audience Segments', '["2-4-audience-segments","perazzi-brand-ethos-personality-ai-reference-2-key-concepts-glossary-2-4-audience-segments"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:51:25.853025+00', null), ('d2486c84-7190-47e9-a97a-a4c780002b25', '6a033257-810e-408f-bcd1-5e0ba6cb7594', '15', '32', '- **High-Complexity Aesthetics**  
  - Examples: highly detailed bulino engraving (e.g., portraits, dogs, scenes), unusual wood grades, complex inlays, and non-standard stock carving.  
  - Typically require more time and specialized engravers or stockmakers.

**Design response:**

- Evaluate whether requested aesthetics can be delivered within the promised timeframe (e.g., a 4-month build window).  
- Communicate clearly if a request adds significant time (e.g., “This bulino engraving may add ~6 months to delivery”).  
- Align on whether the client prioritizes **delivery date** or **aesthetic detail**.', null, '3.4.4 Aesthetics vs Timeline / Cost', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.A > 3. Main Content > 3.4 Typical Decisions & Trade-Offs > 3.4.4 Aesthetics vs Timeline / Cost', '["3-4-4-aesthetics-vs-timeline-cost","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-a-3-main-content-3-4-typical-decisions-trade-offs-3-4-4-aesthetics-vs-timeline-cost"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:54:25.67313+00', null), ('d307fac7-bc64-4f4d-a04b-0f41086e9ae0', '500269f5-9624-4f5b-9ded-8de9740793b2', '6', '7', 'To ensure you are purchasing a genuine and unaltered Perazzi shotgun:

- Purchase only from authorized Perazzi dealers or trusted sources.  
