- May require custom staining, selective sanding, and finish layering to blend new and old.', null, '4.3 Replacement or Repair Work', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.I > 4. Edge Cases, Exceptions, and Caveats > 4.3 Replacement or Repair Work', '["4-3-replacement-or-repair-work","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-i-4-edge-cases-exceptions-and-caveats-4-3-replacement-or-repair-work"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:56:22.593132+00', null), ('e0b61e35-80bd-4fe3-887e-a93cb6856234', '1ae4b60f-6ad5-4475-9eb9-cabf6b0e829c', '26', '56', '- **Default Spec**  
