- Key themes: legacy, identity, pursuit of mastery, lineage of champions, artisan craftsmanship.  
- Story arcs (used in TCN) often follow phases such as **initiation → immersion → revelation → culmination**.[65][66]', null, '3.5.2 Narrative Tone and Style', 'Perazzi Brand Bible – AI Reference > 3. Main Content > 3.5 Brand Philosophy and Ethos > 3.5.2 Narrative Tone and Style', '["3-5-2-narrative-tone-and-style","perazzi-brand-bible-ai-reference-3-main-content-3-5-brand-philosophy-and-ethos-3-5-2-narrative-tone-and-style"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:51:07.263026+00', null), ('ee4faa95-c21e-48e3-802a-150480dd7e9a', '67ca387d-48bc-4047-9404-209a02645c52', '30', '39', '- Historical pattern:
  - Perazzi occasionally introduces innovations (e.g., **adjustable ribs**, **interchangeable trigger blades**, high adjustable ribs) with little prior public discussion.
- Likely ongoing areas (based on industry trends, not confirmed specifics):
  - Alternative materials (e.g., limited titanium receiver experiments).
