  - Trigger and recoil system refinements.
- Unknown:
  - Current projects, prototypes, and experimental results.
- Principle:
  - New work remains **internal** until Perazzi decides to make it public (e.g., at trade shows like IWA or SHOT).', null, '3.3.4 Emerging Innovations and R&D', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part IV: Perazzi vs General Gunmaking > 3. Main Content > 3.3 Unknowns & Respect for Proprietary Knowledge > 3.3.4 Emerging Innovations and R&D', '["3-3-4-emerging-innovations-and-r-d","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-iv-perazzi-vs-general-gunmaking-3-main-content-3-3-unknowns-respect-for-proprietary-knowledge-3-3-4-emerging-innovations-and-r-d"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:58:41.686758+00', null), ('ee5359a9-2752-4e4b-ae03-4859ed9dae1e', '1ae4b60f-6ad5-4475-9eb9-cabf6b0e829c', '19', '56', '- Follow a **repeatable checklist** covering:  
  - Lock-up and lever position.  
  - Trigger and safety function (including selector).  
  - Firing pin strike and rebound.  
  - Ejector and extraction tests (both barrels, individually and together).  
  - Basic balance and weight check.  
- Maintain discipline: every gun passes the same sequence, minimizing risk of missed checks.', null, '3.3.8 Systematic Test Procedures', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.J > 3. Main Content > 3.3 Core Knowledge & Skills > 3.3.8 Systematic Test Procedures', '["3-3-8-systematic-test-procedures","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-j-3-main-content-3-3-core-knowledge-skills-3-3-8-systematic-test-procedures"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:56:46.826724+00', null), ('ee735120-3ae1-4809-b177-2be407ee4ae3', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '119', '238', 'Model name: High Tech SCO | Base model: high-tech | Platform: HT | Category: competition | Disciplines: All Disciplines | Engraving Grade: SCO | Combo configuration: no | Gauges: 12ga, 20ga | Barrel configuration style: over-under | Trigger: removable | Trigger springs: flat, coil | Rib: fixed | Rib style: flat, step, ramp', null, '### High Tech SCO', 'Models > High Tech SCO', '["model-details","high-tech-sco","platform:ht"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('eec563c0-7fac-4bf4-a8ea-d50ba0bd52b0', '4ae532ea-bef9-47fe-9bd9-051858902e2f', '7', '23', '- Part II is the **factory floor tour**, organized from design to final inspection.  
