d2-91d0-41e7-aab7-e2b38cb70931', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '193', '238', 'Model name: MX28 SC3 Sideplates | Base model: mx28 | Platform: MX | Category: game | Disciplines: Game | Engraving Grade: SC3 Sideplates | Combo configuration: no | Gauges: 28ga | Barrel configuration style: over-under | Trigger: fixed | Trigger springs: coil | Rib: fixed', null, '### MX28 SC3 Sideplates', 'Models > MX28 SC3 Sideplates', '["model-details","mx28-sc3-sideplates","platform:mx"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('efa9b2fa-563d-4105-959a-967712173351', 'f8b0315e-200b-46a7-afda-d38cc89aff71', '10', '39', '- **Raw Materials**  
  - Steel bar stock for barrel tubes.  
  - Steel monobloc blanks for the breech.

- **Material Properties**  
  - Specialty ordnance steel chosen for:  
    - Elasticity (tending to bulge rather than shatter under extreme pressure).  
    - Machinability (for drilling, reaming, and soldering).

- **Design & Specification Data**  
  - Barrel length (e.g., 26", 28", 30", 32").  
  - Rib type (flat, raised, adjustable).  
  - Chamber length (e.g., 2¾" or 3").  
  - Choke specification (fixed constrictions vs. threaded choke system).  
  - Target barrel weight and balance for the model/use case.

- **Machinery & Equipment**  
  - Deep-hole drilling machines (gun drills).  
  - Reamers and hones.  
  - Mandrels or shaping fixtures (if used) for contouring and straightening.  
  - Soldering/brazing tools and temperature control.

- **Joining Materials**  
  - Silver brazing alloys (for high-strength monobloc joints).  
  - Lower-temperature solders (for ribs).  
  - Flux.

- **Fixtures & Jigs**  
  - Alignment and regulation fixtures (e.g., muzzle spacing jigs).  
  - Holding fixtures for soldering and straightening.

- **Skilled Labor & Tacit Knowledge**  
  - Barrel makers’ experience in alignment, straightening, and regulation.  
  - Visual and tactile skills for detecting bends and defects.

- **Measurement & Test Tools**  
  - Bore micrometers, choke gauges, chamber gauges.  
  - Straightness references (light box and target line).  
  - Pattern-testing setups.', null, '3.2.1 Inputs', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.C > 3. Main Content > 3.2 Inputs & Outputs > 3.2.1 Inputs', '["3-2-1-inputs","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-c-3-main-content-3-2-inputs-outputs-3-2-1-inputs"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:54:47.674361+00', null), ('efaad629-92f6-4004-a891-1347a40cd577', '40639b0a-dab7-48fe-8f4f-a017a331ec3e', '18', '45', '- Judging the depth of blue-black and deciding when enough rust-bluing cycles have been completed.  
- Subtle adjustments to process (e.g., solution strength, cycle count) to achieve a consistent, brand-characteristic Perazzi “black-blue” tone.', null, '3.3.7 Eye for Color and Texture', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.H > 3. Main Content > 3.3 Core Knowledge & Skills > 3.3.7 Eye for Color and Texture', '["3-3-7-eye-for-color-and-texture","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-h-3-main-content-3-3-core-knowledge-skills-3-3-7-eye-for-color-and-texture"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:56:02.508279+00', null), ('f00e6fd0-6666-4cb6-bc7a-ae530ddef4d6', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '230', '238', 'Model name: MX8 Vintage | Base model: mx8 | Platform: MX | Category: competition | Disciplines: All Disciplines | Engraving Grade: Standard | Combo configuration: no | Gauges: 12ga, 20ga | Barrel configuration style: over-under | Trigger: removable | Trigger springs: flat, coil | Rib: fixed | Rib height: 4.0 mm | Rib style: step', null, '### MX8 Vintage', 'Models > MX8 Vintage', '["model-details","mx8-vintage","platform:mx"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('f0501c58-4cac-4e0a-9764-201aaacbf048', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '63', '238', 'Model name: High Tech RS SC3 | Base model: high-tech-rs | Platform: HT | Category: competition | Disciplines: Skeet, Sporting | Engraving Grade: SC3 | Combo configuration: yes | Gauges: 12ga | Barrel configuration style: over-under | Trigger: removable | Trigger springs: flat, coil | Rib: adjustable | Rib notches: 4-notch adjustable | Rib height: 10.0 mm | Rib style: notch', null, '### High Tech RS SC3', 'Models > High Tech RS SC3', '["model-details","high-tech-rs-sc3","platform:ht"]', '["Prospect","