- Showing how patterns relate to real targets (e.g., rising trap birds vs crossers).  
  - Explaining what “60/40 high” or “dead-on 50/50” means in practice.

- Differentiating **gun vs shooter** factors:

- If a benched gun prints dead-on but the shooter’s patterns are off, recognizing that stock fit (cast, drop) or mount may be the issue.  
  - Suggesting comb or cast adjustments rather than barrel work when the problem is shooter-specific.', null, '3.3.6 Customer Interaction & Communication (When Present)', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.K > 3. Main Content > 3.3 Core Knowledge & Skills > 3.3.6 Customer Interaction & Communication (When Present)', '["3-3-6-customer-interaction-communication-when-present","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-k-3-main-content-3-3-core-knowledge-skills-3-3-6-customer-interaction-communication-when-present"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:57:15.866317+00', null), ('f339232a-0882-4b1f-b946-e35d37599c6f', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '81', '238', 'Model name: High Tech S 2024 5 | Base model: high-tech-s-5 | Platform: HT | Category: competition | Disciplines: All Disciplines | Engraving Grade: 2024 | Combo configuration: no | Gauges: 12ga, 20ga | Barrel configuration style: over-under | Trigger: fixed | Trigger springs: coil | Rib: adjustable | Rib notches: 5-notch adjustable | Rib height: 24.0 mm | Rib style: notch', null, '### High Tech S 2024 5', 'Models > High Tech S 2024 5', '["model-details","high-tech-s-2024-5","platform:ht"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('f357613e-f54a-4b4a-ab67-4dfe708bc240', '8078a4a0-2d04-41fd-bd01-ecfc4c710fbb', '22', '50', '### Lee Bo-na
