- Each decision in the build reflects the owner’s **values, aspirations, and physical connection** to the tool.  
- The process itself is an affirmation of identity, not just a spec selection.', null, '3.6.1 Bespoke Craftsmanship', 'Perazzi Brand Ethos & Personality – AI Reference > 3. Main Content > 3.6 The Perazzi Experience > 3.6.1 Bespoke Craftsmanship', '["3-6-1-bespoke-craftsmanship","perazzi-brand-ethos-personality-ai-reference-3-main-content-3-6-the-perazzi-experience-3-6-1-bespoke-craftsmanship"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:51:25.853025+00', null), ('ff397d57-2683-489b-935b-c9f9b346b6bc', 'e71c2213-11d3-4fbb-ad08-12dd9cb1fbe1', '38', '49', '- A master pattern tester can glance at a pattern and quickly see:

- POI offset in inches/centimeters at distance.  
  - Whether pattern density matches choke expectations.  
  - Whether any irregularity is likely due to the gun or the ammunition.

- They often **do not need to count pellets**; experience lets them evaluate patterns qualitatively but accurately.', null, '3.7.1 Fast, Accurate Reading of Patterns', 'The Making of a Perazzi Over-Under Shotgun – Part II.K > 3. Main Content > 3.7 What Mastery Looks Like > 3.7.1 Fast, Accurate Reading of Patterns', '["3-7-1-fast-accurate-reading-of-patterns","the-making-of-a-perazzi-over-under-shotgun-part-ii-k-3-main-content-3-7-what-mastery-looks-like-3-7-1-fast-accurate-reading-of-patterns"]', '["Prospect","Owner","Navigation"]', '["Loyalist","Prestige","Analyst","Achiever","Legacy"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:57:15.866317+00', null), ('ff57d41c-ddef-42eb-8912-1d94afc65618', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '216', '238', 'Model name: MX8 SC3 Gold | Base model: mx8 | Platform: MX | Category: competition | Disciplines: All Disciplines | Engraving Grade: SC3 Gold | Combo configuration: no | Gauges: 12ga, 20ga | Barrel configuration style: over-under | Trigger: removable | Trigger springs: flat, coil | Rib: fixed | Rib style: flat, step, ramp', null, '### MX8 SC3 Gold', 'Models > MX8 SC3 Gold', '["model-details","mx8-sc3-gold","platform:mx"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2025-12-11 21:52:48.829876+00', null), ('ff6009b6-6197-423f-953e-ede3f5a57adc', '226d9a88-7f09-43b1-983c-d236d935dd77', '207', '238', 'Model name: MX8 | Base model: mx8 | Platform: MX | Category: competition | Disciplines: Trap | Engraving Grade: Standard | Combo configuration: no | Gauges: 12ga | Barrel configuration style: top-single | Trigger: removable | Trigger springs: flat, coil | Rib: fixed | Rib style: flat, step, ramp', null, '### MX8', 'Models > MX8', '["model-details","mx8","platform:mx"]', '["Prospect","Owner"]', '["Analyst","Achiever","Prestige"]', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, n